"02120100.xhp\n"
"par_id3150717\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/headerfootercontent/buttonBTN_TEXT\">Opens a dialog to assign formats to new or selected text.</ahelp> The <emph>Text Attributes</emph> dialog contains the tab pages <link href=\"text/shared/01/05020100.xhp\"><emph>Font</emph></link>, <link href=\"text/shared/01/05020200.xhp\"><emph>Font Effects</emph></link> and <link href=\"text/shared/01/05020500.xhp\"><emph>Font Position</emph></link>."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/headerfootercontent/buttonBTN_TEXT\">ເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບເພື່ອມອບໝາຍຮູບແບບໃຫ້ກັບຂໍ້ຄວາມໃໝ່ ຫຼື ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ເລືອກ.</ahelp> ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ຄຸນລັກສະນະຂໍ້ຄວາມ</emph> ປະກອບດ້ວຍແທັບໜ້າ <link href=\"text/shared/01/05020100.xhp\"><emph>ຟອນ</emph></link>, <link href=\"text/shared/01/05020200.xhp\"><emph>ເອັບເຟັກຟອນ</emph></link> ແລະ <link href=\"text/shared/01/05020500.xhp\"><emph>ຕຳແໜ່ງຟອນ</emph></link>."

#. aSou5
#: 02120100.xhp
