"02140400.xhp\n"
"par_id3150793\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".uno:FillLeft\" visibility=\"visible\">Fills a selected range of at least two columns with the contents of the far right cell.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".uno:FillLeft\" visibility=\"visible\">ຕື່ມຊ່ວງທີ່ເລືອກຢ່າງໜ້ອຍສອງຖັນດ້ວຍເນື້ອໃນຂອງເຊວທີ່ຢູ່ເບື້ອງຂວາສຸດ.</ahelp>"

#. kKTAh
#: 02140400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140400.xhp\n"
"par_id3156280\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If a selected range has only one row, the content of the far right cell is copied into all other cells of the range. If several rows are selected, the far right cells are copied into the cells to the left."
msgstr "ຖ້າຊ່ວງທີ່ເລືອກມີພຽງແຖວດຽວ, ເນື້ອໃນຂອງເຊວເບື້ອງຂວາສຸດຈະຖືກສຳເນົາເຂົ້າໄປໃນເຊວອື່ນໆທັງໝົດຂອງຊ່ວງນັ້ນ. ຖ້າເລືອກຫຼາຍແຖວ, ເຊວເບື້ອງຂວາສຸດຈະຖືກສຳເນົາເຂົ້າໄປໃນເຊວທາງດ້ານຊ້າຍ."

#. 2u4eT
#: 02140500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140500.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Fill Sheets"
msgstr "ຕື່ມໃສ່ແຜ່ນງານ"

#. zC9fM
#: 02140500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140500.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153897\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/scalc/01/02140500.xhp#fill sheets\">Fill Sheets</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/scalc/01/02140500.xhp#fill sheets\">ຕື່ມໃສ່ແຜ່ນງານ</link>"

#. Ccf2V
#: 02140500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140500.xhp\n"
"par_id3150791\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"tabellenfuellentext\"><ahelp hid=\".uno:FillTable\">Specifies the options for transferring sheets or ranges of a certain sheet to the same cells on other selected sheets.</ahelp></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"tabellenfuellentext\"><ahelp hid=\".uno:FillTable\">ກຳນົດຕົວເລືອກສຳລັບການສົ່ງຕໍ່ແຜ່ນງານ ຫຼື ຊ່ວງຂອງແຜ່ນງານໃດໜຶ່ງ ໄປຫາເຊວດຽວກັນໃນແຜ່ນງານອື່ນທີ່ເລືອກ.</ahelp></variable>"

#. Xfzhx
#: 02140500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140500.xhp\n"
"par_id3150768\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This menu command is only active if you have selected at least two sheets in the document."
msgstr "ຄຳສັ່ງເມນູນີ້ຈະໃຊ້ງານໄດ້ກໍຕໍ່ເມື່ອທ່ານເລືອກຢ່າງໜ້ອຍສອງແຜ່ນງານໃນເອກະສານ."

#. Bvr8F
#: 02140500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140500.xhp\n"
"par_id3150769\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To select multiple sheets, click each sheet tab while pressing <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline> or <keycode>Shift</keycode>."
msgstr "ເພື່ອເລືອກຫຼາຍແຜ່ນງານ, ໃຫ້ຄລິກແຕ່ລະແທັບແຜ່ນງານໃນຂະນະທີ່ກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline> ຫຼື <keycode>Shift</keycode> ຄ້າງໄວ້."

#. FYuCU
#: 02140500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140500.xhp\n"
"par_id3150767\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In contrast to copying an area to the clipboard, you can filter certain information and calculate values."
msgstr "ໃນທາງກົງກັນຂ້າມກັບການສຳເນົາເຂດໃດໜຶ່ງໄປຫາຄລິບບອດ, ທ່ານສາມາດກັ່ນຕອງຂໍ້ມູນບາງຢ່າງ ແລະ ຄິດໄລ່ຄ່າໄດ້."

#. oCYjU
#: 02140500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140500.xhp\n"
"hd_id3155131\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Filling a Sheet"
msgstr "ການຕື່ມແຜ່ນງານ"

#. yvAcM
#: 02140500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140500.xhp\n"
"par_id3146119\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the entire sheet by clicking the empty gray box in the upper left of the sheet. You can also select an area of the sheet to be copied."
msgstr "ເລືອກແຜ່ນງານທັງໝົດໂດຍການຄລິກກ່ອງສີເທົາຫວ່າງເປົ່າຢູ່ເບື້ອງຊ້າຍເທິງຂອງແຜ່ນງານ. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເລືອກເຂດຂອງແຜ່ນງານທີ່ຈະສຳເນົາໄດ້."

#. ZhzbN
#: 02140500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140500.xhp\n"
"par_id3153726\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline> and click the tab of the sheet where you want to insert the contents."
msgstr "ກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline> ແລະ ຄລິກແທັບຂອງແຜ່ນງານທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການແຊກເນື້ອໃນ."

#. medyk
#: 02140500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140500.xhp\n"
"par_id3147436\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the command <menuitem>Sheet - Fill Cells - Sheets</menuitem>. In the dialog which appears, the check box <emph>Numbers</emph> must be selected (or <emph>Paste All</emph>) if you want to combine operations with the values. You can also choose the desired operation here."
msgstr "ເລືອກຄຳສັ່ງ <menuitem>ແຜ່ນງານ - ຕື່ມເຊວ - ແຜ່ນງານ</menuitem>. ໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບທີ່ປາກົດຂຶ້ນ, ຊ່ອງໝາຍເລືອກ <emph>ຕົວເລກ</emph> ຕ້ອງຖືກເລືອກ (ຫຼື <emph>ວາງທັງໝົດ</emph>) ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການລວມການດຳເນີນການກັບຄ່າຕ່າງໆ. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເລືອກການດຳເນີນການທີ່ຕ້ອງການໄດ້ທີ່ນີ້."

#. yNrLG
#: 02140500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140500.xhp\n"
"par_id3154942\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click <emph>OK</emph>."
msgstr "ຄລິກ <emph>ຕົກລົງ</emph>."

#. d5MJG
#: 02140500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140500.xhp\n"
"par_id3156283\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This dialog is similar to the <link href=\"text/shared/01/02070000.xhp\"><emph>Paste Special</emph></link> dialog, where you can find additional tips."
msgstr "ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບນີ້ຄ້າຍຄືກັບກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <link href=\"text/shared/01/02070000.xhp\"><emph>ວາງແບບພິເສດ</emph></link>, ເຊິ່ງທ່ານສາມາດຊອກຫາຄຳແນະນຳເພີ່ມເຕີມໄດ້."

#. B6GAM
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Fill Series"
msgstr "ຕື່ມລຳດັບ"

#. 832ME
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"hd_id3148664\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/scalc/01/02140600.xhp#fill series\">Fill Series</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/scalc/01/02140600.xhp#fill series\">ຕື່ມລຳດັບ</link>"

#. c5WSy
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"par_id3148797\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"reihenfuellentext\"><ahelp hid=\".uno:FillSeries\">Automatically generate series with the options in this dialog. Determine direction, increment, time unit and series type.</ahelp></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"reihenfuellentext\"><ahelp hid=\".uno:FillSeries\">ສ້າງລຳດັບໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດດ້ວຍຕົວເລືອກໃນກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບນີ້. ກຳນົດທິດທາງ, ຄ່າເພີ່ມ, ຫົວໜ່ວຍເວລາ ແລະ ປະເພດລຳດັບ.</ahelp></variable>"

#. WnPsX
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"par_id3146976\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Before filling a series, first select the cell range."
msgstr "ກ່ອນທີ່ຈະຕື່ມລຳດັບ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຊ່ວງເຊວກ່ອນ."

#. JjBdD
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"par_id3145748\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To automatically continue a series using the assumed completion rules, choose the <emph>AutoFill</emph> option after opening the <emph>Fill Series</emph> dialog."
msgstr "ເພື່ອກ້າວຕໍ່ລຳດັບໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດໂດຍໃຊ້ກົດເກນການເຮັດໃຫ້ສຳເລັດທີ່ຄາດໄວ້, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຕົວເລືອກ <emph>ຕື່ມອັດຕະໂນມັດ</emph> ຫຼັງຈາກເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ຕື່ມລຳດັບ</emph>."

#. TVJyD
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147435\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Direction"
msgstr "ທິດທາງ"

#. PKotC
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"par_id3154729\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Determines the direction of series creation."
msgstr "ກຳນົດທິດທາງຂອງການສ້າງລຳດັບ."

#. JzPj3
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"hd_id3145253\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Down"
msgstr "ລົງ"

#. hC6AJ
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"par_id3155418\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/filldlg/down\">Creates a downward series in the selected cell range for the column using the defined increment to the end value.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/filldlg/down\">ສ້າງລຳດັບລົງລຸ່ມໃນຊ່ວງເຊວທີ່ເລືອກສຳລັບຖັນໂດຍໃຊ້ຄ່າເພີ່ມທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໄປຫາຄ່າສິ້ນສຸດ.</ahelp>"

#. ekeVg
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"hd_id3155738\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Right"
msgstr "ຂວາ"

#. W9RNB
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"par_id3149402\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/filldlg/right\">Creates a series running from left to right within the selected cell range using the defined increment to the end value.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/filldlg/right\">ສ້າງລຳດັບທີ່ແລ່ນຈາກຊ້າຍໄປຂວາພາຍໃນຊ່ວງເຊວທີ່ເລືອກໂດຍໃຊ້ຄ່າເພີ່ມທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໄປຫາຄ່າສິ້ນສຸດ.</ahelp>"

#. KAZnk
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"hd_id3146972\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Up"
msgstr "ຂຶ້ນ"

#. kWGCK
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"par_id3153711\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/filldlg/up\">Creates an upward series in the cell range of the column using the defined increment to the end value.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/filldlg/up\">ສ້າງລຳດັບຂຶ້ນເທິງໃນຊ່ວງເຊວຂອງຖັນໂດຍໃຊ້ຄ່າເພີ່ມທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໄປຫາຄ່າສິ້ນສຸດ.</ahelp>"

#. 77twa
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"hd_id3153764\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Left"
msgstr "ຊ້າຍ"

#. sbSLo
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"par_id3156382\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/filldlg/left\">Creates a series running from right to left in the selected cell range using the defined increment to the end value.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/filldlg/left\">ສ້າງລຳດັບທີ່ແລ່ນຈາກຂວາໄປຊ້າຍໃນຊ່ວງເຊວທີ່ເລືອກໂດຍໃຊ້ຄ່າເພີ່ມທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໄປຫາຄ່າສິ້ນສຸດ.</ahelp>"

#. fh5PT
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147344\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Series Type"
msgstr "ປະເພດລຳດັບ"

#. Qugvk
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"par_id3149257\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Defines the series type. Choose between <emph>Linear</emph>, <emph>Growth</emph>, <emph>Date</emph> and <emph>AutoFill</emph>."
msgstr "ກຳນົດປະເພດລຳດັບ. ເລືອກລະຫວ່າງ <emph>ເສັ້ນຊື່</emph>, <emph>ການເຕີບໂຕ</emph>, <emph>ວັນທີ</emph> ແລະ <emph>ຕື່ມອັດຕະໂນມັດ</emph>."

#. yfoVv
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"hd_id3148488\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Linear"
msgstr "ເສັ້ນຊື່"

#. 3H2CX
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"par_id3159238\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/filldlg/linear\">Creates a linear number series using the defined increment and end value.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/filldlg/linear\">ສ້າງລຳດັບຕົວເລກແບບເສັ້ນຊື່ໂດຍໃຊ້ຄ່າເພີ່ມ ແລະ ຄ່າສິ້ນສຸດທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້.</ahelp>"

#. XwQDp
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149210\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Growth"
msgstr "ການເຕີບໂຕ"

#. UtVZv
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"par_id3150364\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/filldlg/growth\">Creates a growth series using the defined increment and end value.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/filldlg/growth\">ສ້າງລຳດັບການເຕີບໂຕໂດຍໃຊ້ຄ່າເພີ່ມ ແລະ ຄ່າສິ້ນສຸດທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້.</ahelp>"

#. ydcZJ
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"hd_id3149528\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Date"
msgstr "ວັນທີ"

#. A88kj
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"par_id3150887\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/filldlg/date\">Creates a date series using the defined increment and end date.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/filldlg/date\">ສ້າງລຳດັບວັນທີໂດຍໃຊ້ຄ່າເພີ່ມ ແລະ ວັນທີສິ້ນສຸດທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້.</ahelp>"

#. b7qsB
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150202\n"
"help.text"
msgid "AutoFill"
msgstr "ຕື່ມອັດຕະໂນມັດ"

#. FSwFS
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"par_id3156288\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/filldlg/autofill\">Forms a series directly in the sheet.</ahelp> The <emph>AutoFill</emph> function takes account of customized lists. For example, by entering <emph>January</emph> in the first cell, the series is completed using the list defined under <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - Sort Lists</emph>."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/filldlg/autofill\">ສ້າງລຳດັບໂດຍກົງໃນແຜ່ນງານ.</ahelp> ຟັງຊັນ <emph>ຕື່ມອັດຕະໂນມັດ</emph> ຈະຄຳນຶງເຖິງລາຍການທີ່ປັບແຕ່ງເອງ. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ໂດຍການປ້ອນ <emph>ມັງກອນ</emph> ໃນເຊວທຳອິດ, ລຳດັບຈະຖືກເຮັດໃຫ້ສຳເລັດໂດຍໃຊ້ລາຍການທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ພາຍໃຕ້ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - ສິ່ງທີ່ມັກ</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - %PRODUCTNAME Calc - ຈັດລຽງລາຍການ</emph>."

#. 3bnJA
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"par_id3155811\n"
"help.text"
msgid "AutoFill tries to complete a value series by using a defined pattern. The series 1,3,5 is automatically completed with 7,9,11,13, and so on. Date and time series are completed accordingly; for example, after 1999-01-01 and 1999-01-15, an interval of 14 days is used."
msgstr "ຕື່ມອັດຕະໂນມັດພະຍາຍາມເຮັດໃຫ້ລຳດັບຄ່າສຳເລັດໂດຍການໃຊ້ຮູບແບບທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້. ລຳດັບ 1, 3, 5 ຈະຖືກເຮັດໃຫ້ສຳເລັດໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດດ້ວຍ 7, 9, 11, 13 ແລະ ຕໍ່ໆໄປ. ລຳດັບວັນທີ ແລະ ເວລາຈະຖືກເຮັດໃຫ້ສຳເລັດຕາມນັ້ນ; ຕົວຢ່າງ: ຫຼັງຈາກ 1999-01-01 ແລະ 1999-01-15, ໄລຍະຫ່າງ 14 ວັນຈະຖືກນຳໃຊ້."

#. BQYjs
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"hd_id3148700\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Unit of Time"
msgstr "ຫົວໜ່ວຍເວລາ"

#. Nr8qs
#: 02140600.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140600.xhp\n"
"par_id3153308\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In this area you can specify the desired unit of time. This area is only active if the <emph>Date</emph> option has been chosen in the <emph>Series type</emph> area."
msgstr "ໃນເຂດນີ້ທ່ານສາມາດລະບຸຫົວໜ່ວຍເວລາທີ່ຕ້ອງການ. ເຂດນີ້ຈະໃຊ້ງານໄດ້ກໍຕໍ່ເມື່ອຕົວເລືອກ <emph>ວັນທີ</emph> ຖືກເລືອກໃນເຂດ <emph>ປະເພດລຳດັບ</emph>."

#. o5B68
