msgctxt ""
"02140700.xhp\n"
"par_id2308201415431841782\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Set the initial value of the random number generator to a known value <emph>Seed.</emph></ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ຕັ້ງຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງຕົວສ້າງຕົວເລກສຸ່ມເປັນຄ່າທີ່ຮູ້ຈັກ <emph>ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນສຸ່ມ (Seed).</emph></ahelp>"

#. xkaWC
#: 02140700.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02140700.xhp\n"
