msgctxt ""
"02180000.xhp\n"
"par_id3144764\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/movecopysheet/copy\">Specifies that the sheet is to be copied. If the option is unmarked, the sheet is moved.</ahelp> Moving sheets is the default."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/movecopysheet/copy\">ກຳນົດວ່າຈະໃຫ້ສຳເນົາແຜ່ນງານ. ຖ້າຕົວເລືອກບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກໝາຍ, ແຜ່ນງານຈະຖືກຍ້າຍ.</ahelp> ການຍ້າຍແຜ່ນງານແມ່ນຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ."

