"02190100.xhp\n"
"par_id3154366\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".uno:DeleteRowbreak\">Removes the manual row break above the active cell.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".uno:DeleteRowbreak\">ເອົາການຕັດແຖວດ້ວຍມືທີ່ຢູ່ຂ້າງເທິງເຊວທີ່ໃຊ້ງານຢູ່ອອກ.</ahelp>"

#. aNEE6
#: 02190100.xhp
msgctxt ""
"02190100.xhp\n"
"par_id3151041\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Position the cursor in a cell directly below the row break indicated by a horizontal line and choose <emph>Sheet - Delete Page Break - Row Break</emph>. The manual row break is removed."
msgstr "ວາງເຄີເຊີໃນເຊວທີ່ຢູ່ລຸ່ມການຕັດແຖວໂດຍກົງ ເຊິ່ງສະແດງໂດຍເສັ້ນນອນ ແລະ ເລືອກ <emph>ແຜ່ນງານ - ລຶບການຕັດໜ້າ - ການຕັດແຖວ</emph>. ການຕັດແຖວດ້ວຍມືຈະຖືກເອົາອອກ."

#. Bvrcm
