msgstr "<variable id=\"tabellenauswaehlen\"><ahelp hid=\".uno:SelectTables\" visibility=\"visible\">ເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ເລືອກແຜ່ນງານ</emph> ເພື່ອເລືອກຫຼາຍແຜ່ນງານ.</ahelp></variable>"

