msgctxt ""
"04060104.xhp\n"
"par_id3166442\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<item type=\"input\">=ISLOGICAL(99)</item> returns FALSE, because 99 is a number, not a logical value."
msgstr "<item type=\"input\">=ISLOGICAL(99)</item> ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າ FALSE, ເພາະວ່າ 99 ແມ່ນຕົວເລກ, ບໍ່ແມ່ນຄ່າຕັກກະສາດ."

#. RKxzG
