msgctxt ""
"04060104.xhp\n"
"par_id3556016\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<item type=\"input\">=ISLOGICAL(ISNA(D4))</item> returns TRUE whatever the contents of cell D4, because ISNA() returns a logical value."
msgstr "<item type=\"input\">=ISLOGICAL(ISNA(D4))</item> ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າ TRUE ບໍ່ວ່າເນື້ອໃນໃນຫ້ອງ D4 ຈະແມ່ນຫຍັງກໍຕາມ, ເພາະ ISNA() ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າທາງຕັກກະສາດ."

