"par_id3146155\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This function returns the inverse hyperbolic cotangent of <emph>Number</emph>, that is the number whose hyperbolic cotangent is Number."
msgstr "ຟັງຊັນນີ້ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າໂກຕັງຊັງໄຮເປີໂບລິກປີ້ນຂອງ <emph>ຕົວເລກ</emph>, ນັ້ນຄືຕົວເລກທີ່ມີຄ່າໂກຕັງຊັງໄຮເປີໂບລິກເທົ່າກັບຕົວເລກ."

#. Dr5j2
#: 04060106.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060106.xhp\n"
"par_id5818659\n"
"help.text"
msgid "An error results if Number is between -1 and 1 inclusive."
