msgstr "<image id=\"img_id3150758\" src=\"media/helpimg/scalc/coordinates-to-polar-01.svg\" width=\"2.5inch\" height=\"1.5inch\"><alt id=\"alt_id3150758\">ຕົວຢ່າງພິກັດສາກເປັນພິກັດຂົ້ວ</alt></image>"

