msgctxt ""
"04060106.xhp\n"
"par_id3151285\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<item type=\"input\">=GCD(16;32;24) </item>gives the result 8, because 8 is the largest number that can divide 16, 24 and 32 without a remainder."
msgstr "<item type=\"input\">=GCD(16;32;24) </item>ໃຫ້ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບເປັນ 8, ເພາະວ່າ 8 ແມ່ນຕົວເລກທີ່ໃຫຍ່ທີ່ສຸດທີ່ສາມາດຫານ 16, 24 ແລະ 32 ໄດ້ຂາດ."

#. 2sJeC
#: 04060106.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060106.xhp\n"
"par_id1604663\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<item type=\"input\">=GCD(B1:B3)</item> where cells B1, B2, B3 contain <item type=\"input\">9</item>, <item type=\"input\">12</item>, <item type=\"input\">9</item> gives 3."
msgstr "<item type=\"input\">=GCD(B1:B3)</item> ບ່ອນທີ່ເຊວ B1, B2, B3 ບັນຈຸ <item type=\"input\">9</item>, <item type=\"input\">12</item>, <item type=\"input\">9</item> ຈະໃຫ້ຜົນເປັນ 3."

