#. BB9Ze
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"bm_id3147273\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>matrices; functions</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>Function Wizard; arrays</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>array formulas</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>inline array constants</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>formulas; arrays</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>functions; array functions</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>editing; array formulas</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>copying; array formulas</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>deleting; array formulas</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>adjusting array ranges</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>calculating; conditional calculations</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>matrices; calculations</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>conditional calculations with arrays</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>implicit array handling</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>forced array handling</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ມາຕຣິກ; ຟັງຊັນ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງຟັງຊັນ; ອາເຣ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ສູດອາເຣ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຄ່າຄົງທີ່ອາເຣໃນຕົວ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ສູດ; ອາເຣ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຟັງຊັນ; ຟັງຊັນອາເຣ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການແກ້ໄຂ; ສູດອາເຣ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການກັອບປີ້; ສູດອາເຣ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການລຶບ; ສູດອາເຣ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການປັບຂອບເຂດອາເຣ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການຄຳນວນ; ການຄຳນວນແບບມີເງື່ອນໄຂ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ມາຕຣິກ; ການຄຳນວນ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການຄຳນວນແບບມີເງື່ອນໄຂດ້ວຍອາເຣ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການຈັດການອາເຣແບບໂດຍນັຍ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ການບັງຄັບການຈັດການອາເຣ</bookmark_value>"

#. 8AUFn
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"hd_id3147273\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"arrayfunctit\"><link href=\"text/scalc/01/04060107.xhp\">Array Functions</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"arrayfunctit\"><link href=\"text/scalc/01/04060107.xhp\">ຟັງຊັນອາເຣ</link></variable>"

#. BDGKz
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3154744\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"matrixtext\">This category contains the array functions.</variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"matrixtext\">ໝວດໝູນີ້ບັນຈຸຟັງຊັນຕ່າງໆ ຂອງອາເຣ (Array).</variable>"

#. sWmxg
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"hd_id3146084\n"
"help.text"
msgid "What is an Array?"
msgstr "ອາເຣ (Array) ແມ່ນຫຍັງ?"

#. kisLJ
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3154298\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"wasmatrix\">An array is a linked range of cells on a spreadsheet containing values.</variable> A square range of 3 rows and 3 columns is a 3 x 3 array:"
msgstr "<variable id=\"wasmatrix\">ອາເຣ ແມ່ນຂອບເຂດຂອງຫ້ອງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັນໃນແຜ່ນງານເຊິ່ງບັນຈຸຄ່າຕ່າງໆ ໄວ້.</variable> ຂອບເຂດຮູບຈະຕຸລັດທີ່ມີ 3 ແຖວ ແລະ 3 ຖັນ ເອີ້ນວ່າ ອາເຣ ຂະໜາດ 3 x 3:"

#. NYW8Q
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3153583\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The smallest possible array is a 1 x 2 or 2 x 1 array with two adjacent cells."
msgstr "ອາເຣ ທີ່ນ້ອຍທີ່ສຸດທີ່ເປັນໄປໄດ້ແມ່ນອາເຣ ຂະໜາດ 1 x 2 ຫຼື 2 x 1 ທີ່ມີສອງຫ້ອງຕິດກັນ."

#. 9rqkN
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"hd_id3148474\n"
"help.text"
msgid "What is an array formula?"
msgstr "ສູດອາເຣ (Array Formula) ແມ່ນຫຍັງ?"

#. EBQsz
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3155355\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A formula in which the individual values in a cell range are evaluated is referred to as an array formula. The difference between an array formula and other formulas is that the array formula deals with several values simultaneously instead of just one."
msgstr "ສູດທີ່ປະມວນຜົນຄ່າແຕ່ລະຄ່າໃນຂອບເຂດຫ້ອງຂໍ້ມູນພ້ອມໆ ກັນເອີ້ນວ່າ ສູດອາເຣ. ຄວາມແຕກຕ່າງລະຫວ່າງສູດອາເຣ ແລະ ສູດທົ່ວໄປຄື ສູດອາເຣຈະຈັດການກັບຫຼາຍຄ່າພ້ອມກັນ ແທນທີ່ຈະເຮັດເທື່ອລະຄ່າ."

#. UMVaF
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3151052\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Not only can an array formula process several values, but it can also return several values. The results of an array formula is also an array."
msgstr "ສູດອາເຣບໍ່ພຽງແຕ່ປະມວນຜົນໄດ້ຫຼາຍຄ່າເທົ່ານັ້ນ, ແຕ່ຍັງສາມາດສົ່ງຄ່າຄືນມາໄດ້ຫຼາຍຄ່າໃນເວລາດຽວກັນອີກດ້ວຍ. ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບຂອງສູດອາເຣກໍຄືອາເຣນັ້ນເອງ."

#. hFrtB
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3158432\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To multiply the values in the individual cells by 10 in the above array, you do not need to apply a formula to each individual cell or value. Instead you just need to use a single array formula. Select a range of 3 x 3 cells on another part of the spreadsheet, enter the formula <item type=\"input\">=10*A1:C3</item> and confirm this entry using the key combination <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> + Shift + Enter</emph>. The result is a 3 x 3 array in which the individual values in the cell range (A1:C3) are multiplied by a factor of 10."
msgstr "ເພື່ອຄູນຄ່າໃນແຕ່ລະເຊວດ້ວຍ 10 ໃນອາເຣຂ້າງເທິງ, ທ່ານບໍ່ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງນຳໃຊ້ສູດກັບແຕ່ລະເຊວ ຫຼື ແຕ່ລະຄ່າ. ແທນທີ່ຈະເປັນແບບນັ້ນ, ທ່ານພຽງແຕ່ຕ້ອງໃຊ້ສູດອາເຣດຽວເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ເລືອກຊ່ວງຂອງເຊວ 3 x 3 ໃນສ່ວນອື່ນຂອງສະເປຣດຊີດ, ປ້ອນສູດ <item type=\"input\">=10*A1:C3</item> ແລະ ຢືນຢັນການປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນນີ້ໂດຍໃຊ້ການກົດປຸ່ມປະສົມ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> + Shift + Enter</emph>. ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບແມ່ນອາເຣ 3 x 3 ເຊິ່ງຄ່າແຕ່ລະຄ່າໃນຊ່ວງເຊວ (A1:C3) ຖືກຄູນດ້ວຍ 10."

#. 8NCA2
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3149156\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In addition to multiplication, you can also use other operators on the reference range (an array). With $[officename] Calc, you can add (+), subtract (-), multiply (*), divide (/), use exponents (^), concatenation (&) and comparisons (=, <>, <, >, <=, >=). The operators can be used on each individual value in the cell range and return the result as an array if the array formula was entered."
msgstr "ນອກຈາກການຄູນແລ້ວ, ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດໃຊ້ຕົວດຳເນີນການອື່ນໆ ກັບອາເຣໄດ້ ເຊັ່ນ: ບວກ (+), ລົບ (-), ຫານ (/), ຍົກກຳລັງ (^), ເຊື່ອມຂໍ້ຄວາມ (&) ແລະ ການປຽບທຽບຕ່າງໆ. ຕົວດຳເນີນການເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຈະເຮັດວຽກກັບທຸກຄ່າໃນອາເຣ ແລະ ສົ່ງຜົນໄດ້ຮັບອອກມາເປັນອາເຣໃໝ່."

#. eFkfc
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3166456\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Comparison operators in an array formula treat empty cells in the same way as in a normal formula, that is, either as zero or as an empty string. For example, if cells A1 and A2 are empty the array formulas <item type=\"input\">{=A1:A2=\"\"}</item> and <item type=\"input\">{=A1:A2=0}</item> will both return a 1 column 2 row array of cells containing TRUE."
msgstr "ຕົວດຳເນີນການປຽບທຽບໃນສູດອາເຣຈະປະຕິບັດກັບຫ້ອງວ່າງຄືກັນກັບສູດປົກກະຕິ, ຄືເບິ່ງເປັນສູນ ຫຼື ຂໍ້ຄວາມວ່າງ. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ຖ້າ A1 ແລະ A2 ວ່າງ, ສູດ <item type=\"input\">{=A1:A2=\"\"}</item> ແລະ <item type=\"input\">{=A1:A2=0}</item> ຈະສົ່ງຄ່າ TRUE ທັງສອງຫ້ອງ."

#. rDSKx
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"hd_id3150713\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When do you use array formulas?"
msgstr "ຄວນໃຊ້ສູດອາເຣເມື່ອໃດ?"

#. iQ9Nx
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3149787\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use array formulas if you have to repeat calculations using different values. If you decide to change the calculation method later, you only have to update the array formula. To add an array formula, select the entire array range and then <link href=\"text/scalc/01/04060107.xhp\">make the required change to the array formula</link>."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ສູດອາເຣ ຫາກທ່ານຕ້ອງໄດ້ເຮັດການຄິດໄລ່ຊ້ຳໆ ໂດຍໃຊ້ຄ່າທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນ. ຫາກທ່ານຕັດສິນໃຈປ່ຽນວິທີການຄິດໄລ່ໃນພາຍຫຼັງ, ທ່ານພຽງແຕ່ຕ້ອງອັບເດດສູດອາເຣເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ເພື່ອເພີ່ມສູດອາເຣ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຊ່ວງອາເຣທັງໝົດ ແລ້ວ <link href=\"text/scalc/01/04060107.xhp\">ເຮັດການປ່ຽນແປງທີ່ຈຳເປັນຕໍ່ສູດອາເຣ</link>."

#. vRLSR
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3149798\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Array formulas are also a space saving option when several values must be calculated, since they are not very memory-intensive. In addition, arrays are an essential tool for carrying out complex calculations, because you can have several cell ranges included in your calculations. $[officename] has different math functions for arrays, such as the MMULT function for multiplying two arrays or the SUMPRODUCT function for calculating the scalar products of two arrays."
msgstr "ສູດອາເຣຊ່ວຍປະຢັດເນື້ອທີ່ ແລະ ໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳເມື່ອຕ້ອງຄຳນວນຫຼາຍຄ່າພ້ອມກັນ. ນອກຈາກນັ້ນ, ມັນຍັງເປັນເຄື່ອງມືສຳຄັນສຳລັບການຄຳນວນທີ່ຊັບຊ້ອນ. LibreOffice ມີຟັງຊັນທາງຄະນິດສາດສຳລັບອາເຣໂດຍສະເພາະ ເຊັ່ນ MMULT ສຳລັບການຄູນມາຕຣິກ ຫຼື SUMPRODUCT ສຳລັບຫາຜົນບວກຂອງຜົນຄູນ."

#. BU7BQ
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"hd_id3155588\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Using Array Formulas in $[officename] Calc"
msgstr "ການໃຊ້ສູດອາເຣໃນ $[officename] Calc"

#. YHC4R
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"hd_id651668200191409\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"implicit_intersection_hd\">Implicit intersection of array formulas</variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"implicit_intersection_hd\">ຈຸດຕັດແບບໂດຍນັຍ (Implicit intersection) ຂອງສູດອາເຣ</variable>"

#. M2BM4
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3152876\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can also create a \"normal\" formula in which the reference range, such as parameters, indicate an array formula. This formula is also known as \"implicit intersection\" of array formula. The result is obtained from the intersection of the reference range and the rows or columns in which the formula is found. If there is no intersection or if the range at the intersection covers several rows or columns, a #VALUE! error message appears. The following example illustrates this concept:"
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດສ້າງສູດ \"ປົກກະຕິ\" ທີ່ອ້າງອີງເຖິງຂອບເຂດອາເຣໄດ້, ເຊິ່ງເອີ້ນວ່າ \"ຈຸດຕັດແບບໂດຍນັຍ\". ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບຈະມາຈາກຈຸດຕັດລະຫວ່າງຂອບເຂດທີ່ອ້າງອີງກັບແຖວ ຫຼື ຖັນທີ່ສູດນັ້ນຕັ້ງຢູ່. ຖ້າບໍ່ມີຈຸດຕັດ ຈະສະແດງຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ #VALUE!."

#. Et4mZ
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id631668200233375\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the table above, place the array formula in D1:"
msgstr "ໃນຕາຕະລາງຂ້າງເທິງ, ໃຫ້ໃສ່ສູດອາເຣໃນ D1:"

#. Fb5iF
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id641668200266239\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Cells D1, D2, D3 have values 107, 195, 105 respectively."
msgstr "ຫ້ອງ D1, D2, D3 ຈະມີຄ່າ 107, 195, 105 ຕາມລຳດັບ."

#. EpsqN
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id231668200272420\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Insert the formula below in E2, do not enter as array formula."
msgstr "ໃສ່ສູດລຸ່ມນີ້ໃນ E2, ແຕ່ບໍ່ຕ້ອງໃສ່ເປັນແບບສູດອາເຣ (ບໍ່ຕ້ອງກົດ Ctrl+Shift+Enter)."

#. PhpAa
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id681668200283910\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Cells E1 and E3 are empty, Cell E2 has value 195. This is the implicit intersection of array formulas."
msgstr "ຫ້ອງ E1 ແລະ E3 ຈະວ່າງ, ສ່ວນຫ້ອງ E2 ຈະມີຄ່າ 195. ນີ້ຄືຕົວຢ່າງຂອງຈຸດຕັດແບບໂດຍນັຍ."

#. KdBwt
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id161668200288651\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Insert formula below in E4, as in E2."
msgstr "ໃສ່ສູດລຸ່ມນີ້ໃນ E4, ຄືກັນກັບໃນ E2."

#. G8xZf
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id711668200299613\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Cell E4 display #VALUE!. Row 4 is out of the range A1:A3 of the formula."
msgstr "ຫ້ອງ E4 ຈະສະແດງ #VALUE! ເພາະແຖວທີ 4 ຢູ່ນອກຂອບເຂດ A1:A3 ທີ່ສູດອ້າງອີງເຖິງ."

#. EcJu6
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"hd_id3151271\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Creating Array Formulas"
msgstr "ການສ້າງສູດອາເຣ"

#. keWKE
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3149102\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you create an array formula using the <emph>Function Wizard</emph>, you must mark the <emph>Array</emph> check box each time so that the results are returned in an array. Otherwise, only the value in the upper-left cell of the array being calculated is returned."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານສ້າງສູດອາເຣໂດຍໃຊ້ <emph>ຕົວຊ່ວຍສ້າງຟັງຊັນ</emph>, ທ່ານຕ້ອງໝາຍຕິກໃສ່ຊ່ອງ <emph>ອາເຣ (Array)</emph> ທຸກຄັ້ງ. ຖ້າບໍ່ດັ່ງນັ້ນ, ມັນຈະສະແດງຜົນສະເພາະຫ້ອງຊ້າຍເທິງສຸດຫ້ອງດຽວ."

#. G9EUo
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3153392\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you enter the array formula directly into the cell, you must use the key combination <emph>Shift + </emph><switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> + Enter</emph> instead of the <emph>Enter</emph> key. Only then does the formula become an array formula."
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານປ້ອນສູດອາເຣເຂົ້າໃນຫ້ອງໂດຍກົງ, ທ່ານຕ້ອງໃຊ້ປຸ່ມປະສົມ <emph>Shift + </emph><switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> + Enter</emph> ແທນທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ປຸ່ມ <emph>Enter</emph>. ເມື່ອເຮັດແນວນັ້ນແລ້ວ ສູດຈຶ່ງຈະກາຍເປັນສູດອາເຣ."

#. iGmCa
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3151120\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Array formulas appear in braces in $[officename] Calc. You cannot create array formulas by manually entering the braces."
msgstr "ສູດອາເຣຈະປະກົດຢູ່ໃນວົງຂໍປີກກາ { } ໃນ Calc. ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດສ້າງສູດອາເຣດ້ວຍການພິມວົງຂໍນັ້ນດ້ວຍມືເອງໄດ້."

#. 6zGAy
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3154342\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The cells in a results array are automatically protected against changes. However, you can edit, delete or copy the array formula by selecting the entire array cell range."
msgstr "ຫ້ອງທີ່ຢູ່ໃນອາເຣຜົນໄດ້ຮັບຈະຖືກປ້ອງກັນບໍ່ໃຫ້ແກ້ໄຂແຍກຫ້ອງ. ແຕ່ທ່ານສາມາດແກ້ໄຂ, ລຶບ ຫຼື ກັອບປີ້ໄດ້ໂດຍການເລືອກຂອບເຂດອາເຣທັງໝົດ."

#. 2tDZj
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"hd_id8834803\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Using Inline Array Constants in Formulas"
msgstr "ການໃຊ້ຄ່າຄົງທີ່ອາເຣໃນຕົວ (Inline Array Constants) ໃນສູດ"

#. fuAHa
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id985747\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Calc supports inline matrix/array constants in formulas. An inline array is surrounded by curly braces '{' and '}'. Elements can be each a number (including negatives), a logical constant (TRUE, FALSE), or a literal string. Non-constant expressions are not allowed. Arrays can be entered with one or more rows, and one or more columns. All rows must consist of the same number of elements, all columns must consist of the same number of elements."
msgstr "Calc ຮອງຮັບຄ່າຄົງທີ່ມາຕຣິກ/ອາເຣໃນສູດ. ອາເຣໃນຕົວຈະຖືກຫຸ້ມດ້ວຍວົງຂໍປີກກາ '{' ແລະ '}'. ແຕ່ລະອົງປະກອບສາມາດເປັນຕົວເລກ, ຄ່າທາງໂລຊິກ (TRUE, FALSE), ຫຼື ຂໍ້ຄວາມ. ທຸກແຖວ ແລະ ທຸກຖັນຕ້ອງມີຈຳນວນອົງປະກອບເທົ່າກັນ."

#. CYxYN
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id936613\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The column separator (separating elements in one row) and the row separator are language and locale dependent. But in this help content, the ';' semicolon and '|' pipe symbol are used to indicate the column and row separators, respectively. For example, in the English locale, the ',' comma is used as the column separator, while the ';' semicolon is used as the row separator."
msgstr "ຕົວຂັ້ນຖັນ ແລະ ຕົວຂັ້ນແຖວແມ່ນຂຶ້ນກັບພາສາ ແລະ ພາກພື້ນທີ່ທ່ານໃຊ້. ໃນເນື້ອໃນຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອນີ້, ພວກເຮົາໃຊ້ ';' ເປັນຕົວຂັ້ນຖັນ ແລະ '|' ເປັນຕົວຂັ້ນແຖວ ເປັນຕົວຢ່າງ."

#. 4oGDs
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id936615\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can view and change the row and column separator in <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - Preferences</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Tools - Options</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - Calc - Formula - Separators</emph>."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດເບິ່ງ ແລະ ປ່ຽນແປງຕົວຂັ້ນແຖວ ແລະ ຖັນໄດ້ໃນ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>%PRODUCTNAME - ບຸລິມະສິດ</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວເລືອກ</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> - Calc - ສູດ - ຕົວຂັ້ນ</emph>."

#. pseAZ
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id1877498\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Arrays can not be nested."
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດໃຊ້ ອາເຣ ຊ້ອນ ອາເຣ ໄດ້."

#. frzGa
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id4262520\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Examples:</emph>"
msgstr "<emph>ຕົວຢ່າງ:</emph>"

#. Adzmh
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id9387493\n"
"help.text"
msgid "={1;2;3}"
msgstr "={1;2;3}"

#. CcDoT
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id8207037\n"
"help.text"
msgid "An array with one row consisting of the three numbers 1, 2, and 3."
msgstr "ອາເຣ ທີ່ມີໜຶ່ງແຖວ ເຊິ່ງປະກອບດ້ວຍຕົວເລກສາມຕົວຄື 1, 2, ແລະ 3."

#. WhqRD
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id6757103\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To enter this array constant, you select three cells in a row, then you type the formula <item type=\"input\">={1;2;3}</item> using the curly braces and the semicolons, then press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> + Shift + Enter</emph>."
msgstr "ເພື່ອປ້ອນຄ່າຄົງທີ່ອາເຣນີ້, ໃຫ້ທ່ານເລືອກສາມຫ້ອງໃນແຖວດຽວກັນ, ແລ້ວພິມສູດ <item type=\"input\">={1;2;3}</item> ໂດຍໃຊ້ວົງຂໍປີກກາ ແລະ ເຄື່ອງໝາຍຈ້ຳຈຸດ, ຈາກນັ້ນກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> + Shift + Enter</emph>."

#. uTzcj
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id8868068\n"
"help.text"
msgid "={1;2;3|4;5;6}"
msgstr "={1;2;3|4;5;6}"

#. cTAWF
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id6626483\n"
"help.text"
msgid "An array with two rows and three values in each row."
msgstr "ອາເຣ ທີ່ມີສອງແຖວ ແລະ ແຕ່ລະແຖວມີສາມຄ່າ."

#. BkvQP
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id5262916\n"
"help.text"
msgid "={0;1;2|FALSE;TRUE;\"two\"}"
msgstr "={0;1;2|FALSE;TRUE;\"ສອງ\"}"

#. c4DEy
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id1623889\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A mixed data array."
msgstr "ອາເຣ ທີ່ມີຂໍ້ມູນປະສົມກັນ."

#. x4xmB
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id7781914\n"
"help.text"
msgid "=SIN({1;2;3})"
msgstr "=SIN({1;2;3})"

#. 6LVeK
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id300912\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Entered as a matrix formula, delivers the result of three SIN calculations with the arguments 1, 2, and 3."
msgstr "ເມື່ອປ້ອນເປັນສູດມາຕຣິກ, ຈະໃຫ້ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບຂອງການຄຳນວນ SIN ສາມຄັ້ງ ດ້ວຍຄ່າ 1, 2, ແລະ 3."

#. PDitA
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"hd_id3148660\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Editing Array Formulas"
msgstr "ການແກ້ໄຂສູດອາເຣ"

#. Qi4kV
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3149241\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the cell range or array containing the array formula. To select the whole array, position the cell cursor inside the array range, then press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline> + <keycode>/</keycode>, where <keycode>/</keycode> is the division key on the numeric keypad."
msgstr "ເລືອກຊ່ວງຫ້ອງ ຫຼື ອາເຣ ທີ່ບັນຈຸສູດອາເຣ. ເພື່ອເລືອກອາເຣທັງໝົດ, ໃຫ້ວາງເຄີເຊີຫ້ອງໄວ້ໃນຊ່ວງອາເຣ, ແລ້ວກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline> + <keycode>/</keycode>, ໂດຍທີ່ <keycode>/</keycode> ແມ່ນປຸ່ມຫານໃນແຜງປຸ່ມຕົວເລກ."

#. BzLzG
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3143274\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Either press <emph>F2</emph> or position the cursor in the input line. Both of these actions let you edit the formula."
msgstr "ກົດ <emph>F2</emph> ຫຼື ຄລິກໃສ່ແຖບປ້ອນສູດ ເພື່ອແກ້ໄຂສູດ."

#. A2ZDT
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3154798\n"
"help.text"
msgid "After you have made changes, press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> + Shift + Enter</emph>."
msgstr "ຫຼັງຈາກທີ່ທ່ານໄດ້ເຮັດການປ່ຽນແປງແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>ຄຳສັ່ງ</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> + Shift + Enter</emph>."

#. AKFjm
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3150628\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can format the separate parts of an array. For example, you can change the font color. Select a cell range and then change the attribute you want."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດຮູບແບບບາງສ່ວນຂອງອາເຣໄດ້ ເຊັ່ນ: ປ່ຽນສີຕົວອັກສອນ. ພຽງແຕ່ເລືອກຂອບເຂດຫ້ອງທີ່ຕ້ອງການ ແລ້ວປ່ຽນຮູບແບບຕາມໃຈ."

#. Tes4E
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"hd_id541633516074226\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Deleting Array Formulae"
msgstr "ການລຶບສູດອາເຣ"

#. adAax
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id681633516103267\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the cell range or array containing the array formula. To select the whole array, position the cell cursor inside the array range, then press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline> + <keycode>/</keycode>, where <keycode>/</keycode> is the division key on the numeric keypad."
msgstr "ເລືອກຊ່ວງເຊວ ຫຼື ອາເຣທີ່ບັນຈຸສູດອາເຣ. ເພື່ອເລືອກອາເຣທັງໝົດ, ໃຫ້ວາງເຄີເຊີເຊວໄວ້ໃນຊ່ວງອາເຣ, ແລ້ວກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>ຄຳສັ່ງ</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline> + <keycode>/</keycode>, ໂດຍທີ່ <keycode>/</keycode> ແມ່ນປຸ່ມຫານຢູ່ເທິງແປ້ນພິມຕົວເລກ."

#. QeAAF
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id61633516164519\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press <keycode>Delete</keycode> to delete the array contents, including the array formula, or press <keycode>Backspace</keycode> and this brings up the <link href=\"text/scalc/01/02150000.xhp\">Delete Contents</link> dialog box. Select <emph>Formula</emph> or <emph>Delete All</emph> and click <emph>OK</emph>."
msgstr "ກົດ <keycode>Delete</keycode> ເພື່ອລຶບເນື້ອໃນ ແລະ ສູດອາເຣທັງໝົດ, ຫຼື ກົດ <keycode>Backspace</keycode> ເພື່ອເປີດໜ້າຕ່າງ <link href=\"text/scalc/01/02150000.xhp\">ລຶບເນື້ອໃນ</link>. ເລືອກ <emph>ສູດ</emph> ຫຼື <emph>ລຶບທັງໝົດ</emph> ແລ້ວກົດ <emph>ຕົກລົງ</emph>."

#. dEcVJ
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"hd_id3145608\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Copying Array Formulas"
msgstr "ການກັອບປີ້ສູດອາເຣ"

#. DAJJs
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3149585\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the cell range or array containing the array formula."
msgstr "ເລືອກຂອບເຂດຫ້ອງ ຫຼື ອາເຣທີ່ມີສູດອາເຣນັ້ນຢູ່."

#. onH9W
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3154619\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Either press <emph>F2</emph> or position the cursor in the input line."
msgstr "ກົດ <emph>F2</emph> ຫຼື ຄລິກໃສ່ແຖບປ້ອນສູດ."

#. MTD8j
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3150994\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Copy the formula into the input line by pressing <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> + C</emph>."
msgstr "ຄັດລອກສູດລົງໃນແຖວປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນໂດຍການກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>ຄຳສັ່ງ</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> + C</emph>."

#. 8GbwE
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3146787\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select a range of cells where you want to insert the array formula and either press <emph>F2</emph> or position the cursor in the input line."
msgstr "ເລືອກຂອບເຂດຫ້ອງໃໝ່ທີ່ຕ້ອງການວາງສູດ ແລ້ວກົດ <emph>F2</emph> ຫຼື ຄລິກໃສ່ແຖບປ້ອນສູດ."

#. EBtxq
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3154419\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Paste the formula by pressing <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> + V</emph> in the selected space and confirm it by pressing <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> + Shift + Enter</emph>. The selected range now contains the array formula."
msgstr "ວາງສູດໂດຍການກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> + V</emph> ໃນບ່ອນທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້ ແລະ ຢືນຢັນໂດຍການກົດ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline><emph> + Shift + Enter</emph>. ຕອນນີ້ຊ່ວງທີ່ເລືອກຈະບັນຈຸສູດອາເຣ (array formula)."

#. HehUu
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"hd_id3154834\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Adjusting an Array Range"
msgstr "ການປັບຂອບເຂດອາເຣ"

#. RNWq6
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3148679\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If you want to edit the output array, do the following:"
msgstr "ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການປັບປ່ຽນຂອບເຂດຂອງອາເຣຜົນໄດ້ຮັບ, ໃຫ້ເຮັດດັ່ງນີ້:"

#. FjHFw
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3151102\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the cell range or array containing the array formula."
msgstr "ເລືອກຂອບເຂດອາເຣທີ່ມີສູດຢູ່."

#. HiEAu
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3147096\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Below the selection, to the right, you will see a small icon with which you can zoom in or out on the range using your mouse."
msgstr "ຢູ່ມຸມຂວາລຸ່ມຂອງສ່ວນທີ່ເລືອກ, ທ່ານຈະເຫັນໄອຄອນນ້ອຍໆ ເຊິ່ງທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ເມົາສ໌ລາກເພື່ອຂະຫຍາຍ ຫຼື ຫຍໍ້ຂອບເຂດໄດ້."

#. DKvtE
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3150974\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When you adjust the array range, the array formula will not automatically be adjusted. You are only changing the range in which the result will appear."
msgstr "ເມື່ອທ່ານປັບຂອບເຂດອາເຣ, ສູດອາເຣຈະບໍ່ຖືກປັບປ່ຽນໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ. ທ່ານພຽງແຕ່ປ່ຽນບໍລິເວນທີ່ຈະໃຫ້ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບປະກົດອອກມາເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. DQ5ep
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_id3146080\n"
"help.text"
msgid "By holding down the <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>Command</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline> key, you can create a copy of the array formula in the given range."
msgstr "ໂດຍການກົດປຸ່ມ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><emph>ຄຳສັ່ງ</emph></caseinline><defaultinline><emph>Ctrl</emph></defaultinline></switchinline> ຄ້າງໄວ້, ທ່ານສາມາດສ້າງສຳເນົາຂອງສູດອາເຣໃນຊ່ວງທີ່ກຳນົດໃຫ້."

#. 9MbQS
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_idN10D47\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Conditional Array Calculations"
msgstr "ການຄຳນວນອາເຣແບບມີເງື່ອນໄຂ"

#. 86doB
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_idN10D4B\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A conditional array calculation is an array or matrix formula that includes an IF() or CHOOSE() function. The condition argument in the formula is an area reference or a matrix result."
msgstr "ການຄຳນວນອາເຣແບບມີເງື່ອນໄຂຄືການໃຊ້ສູດອາເຣ ຫຼື ມາຕຣິກ ທີ່ປະກອບມີຟັງຊັນ IF() ຫຼື CHOOSE()."

#. g8Lbq
#: 04060107.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060107.xhp\n"
"par_idN10D4E\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In the following example, the >0 test of the {=IF(A1:A3>0;\"yes\";\"no\")} formula is applied to each cell in the range A1:A3 and the result is copied to the corresponding cell."
msgstr "ໃນຕົວຢ່າງລຸ່ມນີ້, ສູດ {=IF(A1:A3>0;\"yes\";\"no\")} ຈະຖືກກວດສອບກັບທຸກຫ້ອງໃນ A1:A3 ແລະ ສະແດງຜົນໃນຫ້ອງທີ່ກົງກັນ."

