msgctxt ""
"04060111.xhp\n"
"par_id221626469509161\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Refer to the <link href=\"https://wiki.documentfoundation.org/Documentation/Calc_Functions/ROT13\">ROT13</link> wiki page for more details about this function."
msgstr "ເບິ່ງລາຍລະອຽດເພີ່ມເຕີມກ່ຽວກັບຟັງຊັນນີ້ໄດ້ທີ່ ໜ້າວິກິ <link href=\"https://wiki.documentfoundation.org/Documentation/Calc_Functions/ROT13\">ROT13</link>."

