"par_id3149030\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_AAI_FUNC_DEC2HEX\">The result is the string representing the number in hexadecimal form for the number entered.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_AAI_FUNC_DEC2HEX\">ຜົນຮັບແມ່ນຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ສະແດງເຖິງຕົວເລກໃນຮູບແບບເລກຖານສິບຫົກ ຈາກຕົວເລກທີ່ປ້ອນເຂົ້າ.</ahelp>"

