"04060115.xhp\n"
"par_id3149715\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>LowerLimit</emph> is the lower limit of the integral."
msgstr "<emph>LowerLimit</emph> ແມ່ນຂອບເຂດລຸ່ມຂອງອິນທິກຣັລ (integral)."

