msgctxt ""
"04060115.xhp\n"
"par_id3156294\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>UpperLimit</emph> is optional. It is the upper limit of the integral. If this value is missing, the calculation takes place between 0 and the lower limit."
msgstr "<emph>UpperLimit</emph> ແມ່ນທາງເລືອກ. ມັນແມ່ນຂອບເຂດເທິງຂອງອິນທິກຣັລ. ຖ້າບໍ່ໄດ້ລະບຸຄ່ານີ້, ການຄຳນວນຈະເກີດຂຶ້ນລະຫວ່າງ 0 ຫາ ຂອບເຂດລຸ່ມ."

