"par_id3156111\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_AAI_FUNC_COMPLEX\">The result is a complex number which is returned from a real coefficient and an imaginary coefficient.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_AAI_FUNC_COMPLEX\">ຜົນໄດ້ຮັບແມ່ນຈຳນວນສົນ ທີ່ສ້າງຂຶ້ນມາຈາກສໍາປະສິດສ່ວນຈິງ ແລະ ສໍາປະສິດສ່ວນຈິນຕະນາການ.</ahelp>"

