"par_id3150593\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_AAI_FUNC_DOLLARFR\">Converts a quotation that has been given as a decimal number into a mixed decimal fraction.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_AAI_FUNC_DOLLARFR\">ແປງລາຄາອ້າງອີງທີ່ໃຫ້ມາເປັນຕົວເລກທົດສະນິຍົມ ໃຫ້ເປັນເສດສ່ວນທົດສະນິຍົມປະສົມ.</ahelp>"

