"par_id3154111\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>FractionalDollar</emph> is a number given as a decimal fraction."
msgstr "<emph>FractionalDollar</emph> ແມ່ນຕົວເລກທີ່ໃຫ້ມາເປັນເສດສ່ວນທົດສະນິຍົມ."

#. A3rfB
#: 04060119.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060119.xhp\n"
"par_id3153695\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Fraction</emph> is a whole number that is used as the denominator of the decimal fraction."
msgstr "<emph>Fraction</emph> ແມ່ນຕົວເລກຖ້ວນທີ່ໃຊ້ເປັນຕົວສ່ວນຂອງເສດສ່ວນທົດສະນິຍົມ."

#. EVEdB
