msgid "<item type=\"input\">=DOLLARDE(1.02;16)</item> stands for 1 and 2/16. This returns 1.125."
msgstr "<item type=\"input\">=DOLLARDE(1.02;16)</item> ໝາຍເຖິງ 1 ແລະ 2/16. ສິ່ງນີ້ຈະສົ່ງຄ່າຄືນ 1.125."

#. Z3ukC
