msgctxt ""
"04060119.xhp\n"
"par_id3149627\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Price</emph> is the price (purchase price) of the treasury bill per 100 currency units of par value."
msgstr "<emph>Price</emph> ແມ່ນລາຄາ (ລາຄາຊື້) ຂອງພັນທະບັດຄັງເງິນຕໍ່ 100 ຫົວໜ່ວຍສະກຸນເງິນຂອງມູນຄ່າທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້."

