msgid "<emph>Beta</emph> (required) is a parameter to the distribution."
msgstr "<emph>Beta</emph> (ຈຳເປັນ) ແມ່ນພາລາມິເຕີຂອງການແຈກຢາຍ."

#. FY5Mb
#: 04060181.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060181.xhp\n"
"par_id062920141254453\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Cumulative</emph> (required) can be 0 or False to calculate the probability density function. It can be any other value or True to calculate the cumulative distribution function."
msgstr "<emph>Cumulative</emph> (ຈຳເປັນ) ສາມາດເປັນ 0 ຫຼື False ເພື່ອຄິດໄລ່ຟັງຊັນຄວາມໜາແໜ້ນຂອງຄວາມໜ້າຈະເປັນ. ສາມາດເປັນຄ່າອື່ນໆ ຫຼື True ເພື່ອຄິດໄລ່ຟັງຊັນການແຈກຢາຍສະສົມ."

#. LUTm6
#: 04060181.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060181.xhp\n"
"par_id2950254\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Start</emph> (optional) is the lower bound for <emph>Number</emph>."
msgstr "<emph>Start</emph> (ທາງເລືອກ) ແມ່ນຂອບເຂດຕ່ຳສຸດສຳລັບ <emph>Number</emph>."

#. qUy9z
#: 04060181.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060181.xhp\n"
"par_id2949138\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>End</emph> (optional) is the upper bound for <emph>Number</emph>."
msgstr "<emph>End</emph> (ທາງເລືອກ) ແມ່ນຂອບເຂດສູງສຸດສຳລັບ <emph>Number</emph>."

