#. GG7mb
#: 04060182.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060182.xhp\n"
"par_id3155089\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FUNC_FINV\">Returns the inverse of the F probability distribution.</ahelp> The F distribution is used for F tests in order to set the relation between two differing data sets."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FUNC_FINV\">ສົ່ງຄ່າຄືນສ່ວນກັບຂອງການແຈກຢາຍຄວາມໜ້າຈະເປັນ F.</ahelp> ການແຈກຢາຍ F ແມ່ນຖືກໃຊ້ສຳລັບການທົດສອບ F ເພື່ອກຳນົດຄວາມສຳພັນລະຫວ່າງສອງຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ແຕກຕ່າງກັນ."

#. TengJ
#: 04060182.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060182.xhp\n"
"par_id3153068\n"
"help.text"
msgid "FINV(Number; DegreesFreedom1; DegreesFreedom2)"
msgstr "FINV(Number; DegreesFreedom1; DegreesFreedom2)"

