msgctxt ""
"04060182.xhp\n"
"par_id3153914\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>DegreesFreedom1</emph> is the number of degrees of freedom in the numerator of the F distribution."
msgstr "<emph>DegreesFreedom1</emph> ແມ່ນຈຳນວນອົງສາເສລີໃນຕົວເສດຂອງການແຈກຢາຍ F."

