"04060182.xhp\n"
"par_id3149819\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<item type=\"input\">=GEOMEAN(23;46;69)</item> = 41.79. The geometric mean value of this random sample is therefore 41.79."
msgstr "<item type=\"input\">=GEOMEAN(23;46;69)</item> = 41.79. ດັ່ງນັ້ນ, ຄ່າສະເລ່ຍເລຂາຄະນິດຂອງກຸ່ມຕົວຢ່າງນີ້ແມ່ນ 41.79."

#. orW9n
