msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FUNC_HARMITTEL\">Returns the harmonic mean of a data set.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FUNC_HARMITTEL\">ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າສະເລ່ຍຮາໂມນິກຂອງຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນ.</ahelp>"

