"04060182.xhp\n"
"par_id2948827\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Cumulative </emph>: 0 or False calculates the probability density function. Other values or True calculates the cumulative distribution function."
msgstr "<emph>Cumulative </emph>: 0 ຫຼື False ແມ່ນຄິດໄລ່ຕຳລາຄວາມໜາແໜ້ນຄວາມໜ້າຈະເປັນ. ຄ່າອື່ນໆ ຫຼື True ແມ່ນຄິດໄລ່ຕຳລາການແຈກຢາຍສະສົມ."

#. xhCCb
