#. DqcAB
#: 04060183.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060183.xhp\n"
"par_id3149872\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Alpha</emph> is the level of the confidence interval."
msgstr "<emph>Alpha</emph> ແມ່ນລະດັບຂອງຊ່ວງຄວາມເຊື່ອໝັ້ນ."

#. CBEqd
