msgctxt ""
"04060184.xhp\n"
"par_id3148878\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>SP</emph> is the probability of the success of an attempt."
msgstr "<emph>SP</emph> ແມ່ນຄວາມໜ້າຈະເປັນຂອງຄວາມສຳເລັດໃນການທົດລອງ."

#. J26hB
