msgctxt ""
"04060184.xhp\n"
"par_id2948879\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Cumulative</emph> = 0 calculates the density function, <emph>Cumulative</emph> = 1 calculates the distribution."
msgstr "<emph>Cumulative</emph> = 0 ແມ່ນຄິດໄລ່ຕຳລາຄວາມໜາແໜ້ນ, <emph>Cumulative</emph> = 1 ແມ່ນຄິດໄລ່ຕຳລາການແຈກຢາຍ."

