#. QjCGT
#: 04060185.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060185.xhp\n"
"par_id2954951\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Cumulative</emph> 0 or FALSE calculates the probability density function. Any other value or TRUE calculates the cumulative distribution function."
msgstr "<emph>Cumulative</emph> 0 ຫຼື FALSE ຄິດໄລ່ຟັງຊັນຄວາມໜາແໜ້ນຂອງຄວາມໜ້າຈະເປັນ. ຄ່າອື່ນໆ ຫຼື TRUE ຄິດໄລ່ຟັງຊັນການແຈກຢາຍສະສົມ."

