#. Bwv8X
#: 04060185.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060185.xhp\n"
"par_id3150386\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FUNC_STEIGUNG\">Returns the slope of the linear regression line.</ahelp> The slope is adapted to the data points set in the y and x values."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FUNC_STEIGUNG\">ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າຄວາມຊັນ (slope) ຂອງເສັ້ນຖົດຖອຍແບບເສັ້ນຊື່.</ahelp> ຄວາມຊັນຈະຖືກປັບໃຫ້ເຂົ້າກັບຈຸດຂໍ້ມູນໃນຄ່າ y ແລະ x."

