"par_id3154748\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FUNC_SUMQUADABW\">Returns the sum of squares of deviations based on a sample mean.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FUNC_SUMQUADABW\">ສົ່ງຄືນຜົນບວກຂອງກຳລັງສອງຂອງສ່ວນບ່ຽງເບນ ໂດຍອີງໃສ່ຄ່າສະເລ່ຍຂອງກຸ່ມຕົວຢ່າງ.</ahelp>"

