#. BQQUu
#: 04060185.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060185.xhp\n"
"par_id2853372\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FUNC_TDIST_2T\">Calculates the two-tailed Student's T Distribution, which is a continuous probability distribution that is frequently used for testing hypotheses on small sample data sets.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FUNC_TDIST_2T\">ຄິດໄລ່ການແຈກຢາຍທີຂອງສະຕິວເດັນ (Student's T Distribution) ແບບສອງດ້ານ, ເຊິ່ງແມ່ນການແຈກຢາຍຄວາມໜ້າຈະເປັນແບບຕໍ່ເນື່ອງທີ່ມັກໃຊ້ເພື່ອທົດສອບສົມມຸດຕິຖານໃນຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນກຸ່ມຕົວຢ່າງຂະໜາດນ້ອຍ.</ahelp>"

#. WoA66
#: 04060185.xhp
msgctxt ""
"04060185.xhp\n"
"par_id2850521\n"
"help.text"
msgid "T.DIST.2T(Number; DegreesFreedom)"
