msgstr "<link href=\"https://docs.oasis-open.org/office/OpenDocument/v1.3/os/part4-formula/OpenDocument-v1.3-os-part4-formula.html#Operators\">OpenDocument v1.3 ພາກທີ 4, ຕົວດຳເນີນການສູດ</link>"

#. LfJJp
