#. XGN2E
#: 05030300.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05030300.xhp\n"
"par_id8337046\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Select the range that includes the hidden objects. You can also use the box in the corner above row 1 and beside column A."
msgstr "ເລືອກຊ່ວງທີ່ຮວມເອົາວັດຖຸທີ່ຖືກເຊື່ອງໄວ້. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດໃຊ້ຊ່ອງໃນມຸມເທິງແຖວທີ 1 ແລະ ຂ້າງຖັນ A ໄດ້."

#. jAJmG
