"par_id3153092\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can also open the<emph> Rename Sheet </emph>dialog through the context menu by positioning the mouse pointer over a sheet tab at the bottom of the window and <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">clicking while pressing Control</caseinline><defaultinline>clicking the right mouse button</defaultinline></switchinline>."
msgstr "ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເປີດກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <emph>ປ່ຽນຊື່ຊີດ</emph> ຜ່ານເມນູລັດໂດຍການວາງເມົາສ໌ໄວ້ເທິງແຖບຊີດຢູ່ທາງລຸ່ມຂອງໜ້າຕ່າງ ແລະ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\">ຄລິກພ້ອມກັບກົດປຸ່ມ Control</caseinline><defaultinline>ຄລິກປຸ່ມຂວາຂອງເມົາສ໌</defaultinline></switchinline>."

#. 6mAmV
#: 05050100.xhp
msgctxt ""
