#. osYik
#: 05070500.xhp
msgctxt ""
"05070500.xhp\n"
"par_id3125863\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Defines which elements of the spreadsheet are to be printed."
msgstr "ກຳນົດວ່າອົງປະກອບໃດຂອງສະເປຣດຊີດທີ່ຈະຖືກພິມອອກມາ."

#. MbbQo
