#. xpA7W
#: 06030900.xhp
msgctxt ""
"06030900.xhp\n"
"par_id3151041\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If <emph>Tools - Detective - AutoRefresh</emph> is turned on, every time formulas are changed in the document."
msgstr "ຖ້າ <emph>ເຄື່ອງມື - ຕົວສືບຄົ້ນ - ຟື້ນຟູອັດຕະໂນມັດ</emph> ຖືກເປີດໄວ້, ທຸກຄັ້ງທີ່ສູດໃນເອກະສານຖືກປ່ຽນແປງ."

#. rftbG
