"12050200.xhp\n"
"par_id3147317\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/subtotaloptionspage/pagebreak\">Inserts a new page after each group of subtotaled data.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/subtotaloptionspage/pagebreak\">ແຊກໜ້າໃໝ່ຫຼັງຈາກແຕ່ລະກຸ່ມຂອງຂໍ້ມູນຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍ.</ahelp>"

#. xcM2E
#: 12050200.xhp
msgctxt ""
"12050200.xhp\n"
"hd_id3146985\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Case sensitive"
msgstr "ກວດສອບຕົວພິມໃຫຍ່-ນ້ອຍ"

#. iVzqn
#: 12050200.xhp
msgctxt ""
"12050200.xhp\n"
"par_id3153190\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/subtotaloptionspage/case\">Recalculates subtotals when you change the case of a data label.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/subtotaloptionspage/case\">ຄຳນວນຜົນລວມຍ່ອຍໃໝ່ເມື່ອທ່ານປ່ຽນຕົວພິມໃຫຍ່-ນ້ອຍຂອງປ້າຍຊື່ຂໍ້ມູນ.</ahelp>"

#. qDCGN
#: 12050200.xhp
msgctxt ""
"12050200.xhp\n"
"hd_id3151119\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Pre-sort area according to groups"
msgstr "ລຽງລຳດັບພື້ນທີ່ລ່ວງໜ້າຕາມກຸ່ມ"

#. vpMJn
#: 12050200.xhp
msgctxt ""
"12050200.xhp\n"
"par_id3149664\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/subtotaloptionspage/sort\">Sorts the area that you selected in the <emph>Group by</emph> box of the Group tabs according to the columns that you selected.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/subtotaloptionspage/sort\">ລຽງລຳດັບພື້ນທີ່ທີ່ທ່ານເລືອກໃນກ່ອງ <emph>ຈັດກຸ່ມຕາມ</emph> ຂອງແຖບກຸ່ມ ຕາມຄໍລຳທີ່ທ່ານເລືອກ.</ahelp>"

#. 86z3r
#: 12050200.xhp
msgctxt ""
"12050200.xhp\n"
"hd_id111758840258673\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Summary below data"
msgstr "ບົດສະຫຼຸບໄວ້ກ້ອງຂໍ້ມູນ"

#. CQVLq
#: 12050200.xhp
msgctxt ""
"12050200.xhp\n"
"par_id571758840533603\n"
"help.text"
msgid "By default, the summary appears above the data. When selected, it moves below the data."
msgstr "ໂດຍປົກກະຕິ, ບົດສະຫຼຸບຈະປະກົດຢູ່ເທິງຂໍ້ມູນ. ເມື່ອເລືອກອັນນີ້, ມັນຈະຍ້າຍໄປຢູ່ກ້ອງຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. 6o48R
