msgstr "ຊ່ວງການລວບລວມ"

#. 9YVBH
#: 12070000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"12070000.xhp\n"
"par_id3151075\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/consolidatedialog/consareas\">Displays the cell ranges that you want to consolidate.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/consolidatedialog/consareas\">ສະແດງຊ່ວງເຊວທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການລວບລວມ.</ahelp>"

#. P3ptZ
