"par_id3154124\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The contents of this dialog is different for data fields in the <emph>Data</emph> area, and data fields in the <emph>Row</emph> or <emph>Column</emph> area of the <link href=\"text/scalc/01/12090102.xhp\">Pivot Table</link> dialog."
msgstr "ເນື້ອໃນຂອງກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບນີ້ຈະແຕກຕ່າງກັນສຳລັບຟິວຂໍ້ມູນໃນພື້ນທີ່ <emph>ຂໍ້ມູນ</emph>, ແລະ ຟິວຂໍ້ມູນໃນພື້ນທີ່ <emph>ແຖວ</emph> ຫຼື <emph>ຄໍລຳ</emph> ຂອງກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບ <link href=\"text/scalc/01/12090102.xhp\">ຕາຕະລາງພິວອດ</link>."

