msgstr "ກຳນົດຈຸດສິ້ນສຸດຂອງການຈັດກຸ່ມ."

#. Kr9BA
#: 12090400.xhp
msgctxt ""
"12090400.xhp\n"
"par_idN10584\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Automatically"
