#. fYiGb
#: 12100000.xhp
msgctxt ""
"12100000.xhp\n"
"par_id3153088\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"aktualisieren\"><ahelp hid=\".\">Updates a data range that was inserted from an external database. The data in the sheet is updated to match the data in the external database.</ahelp></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"aktualisieren\"><ahelp hid=\".\">ອັບເດດຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຖືກນຳເຂົ້າມາຈາກຖານຂໍ້ມູນພາຍນອກ. ຂໍ້ມູນໃນແຜ່ນງານຈະຖືກອັບເດດໃຫ້ກົງກັບຂໍ້ມູນໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນພາຍນອກ.</ahelp></variable>"

#. VRAR6
