"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/validationcriteriapage/ValidationCriteriaPage\">Specify the validation rules for the selected cell(s).</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"modules/scalc/ui/validationcriteriapage/ValidationCriteriaPage\">ກຳນົດກົດເກນການກວດສອບຄວາມຖືກຕ້ອງສຳລັບເຊວທີ່ເລືອກ.</ahelp>"

#. kWDG3
#: 12120100.xhp
