#. j5VoE
#: HandleDuplicateRecords.xhp
msgctxt ""
"HandleDuplicateRecords.xhp\n"
"par_id681725905689582\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Selects or removes the duplicate rows or columns from the selection. The duplicate records dialog has various options."
msgstr "ເລືອກ ຫຼື ລຶບແຖວ ຫຼື ຖັນທີ່ຊ້ຳກັນອອກຈາກການເລືອກ. ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບຈັດການຂໍ້ມູນຊ້ຳມີຕົວເລືອກຕ່າງໆ."

#. BHDWE
#: HandleDuplicateRecords.xhp
msgctxt ""
"HandleDuplicateRecords.xhp\n"
"par_id151725960913414\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Compare:</emph> specifies whether to compare rows or columns."
msgstr "<emph>ປຽບທຽບ:</emph> ກຳນົດວ່າຈະປຽບທຽບແຖວ ຫຼື ຖັນ."

#. yrWBU
#: HandleDuplicateRecords.xhp
msgctxt ""
"HandleDuplicateRecords.xhp\n"
"par_id991725961010287\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Header:</emph> specifies if the selected data includes table headers. If checked, the table headers (the first row or column) are ignored."
msgstr "<emph>ສ່ວນຫົວ:</emph> ກຳນົດວ່າຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ເລືອກນັ້ນລວມມີສ່ວນຫົວຂອງຕາຕະລາງນຳຫຼືບໍ່. ຫາກໝາຍເລືອກ, ສ່ວນຫົວຕາຕະລາງ (ແຖວ ຫຼື ຖັນທຳອິດ) ຈະຖືກລະເວັ້ນ."

#. 7nAND
#: HandleDuplicateRecords.xhp
msgctxt ""
"HandleDuplicateRecords.xhp\n"
"par_id61725963172527\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Compare by:</emph> specifies which fields to compare (and which to ignore) when determining whether two rows or columns are duplicates or not."
msgstr "<emph>ປຽບທຽບໂດຍ:</emph> ກຳນົດວ່າຈະປຽບທຽບເຂດຂໍ້ມູນໃດ (ແລະ ອັນໃດຈະລະເວັ້ນ) ເມື່ອພິຈາລະນາວ່າຍັງມີສອງແຖວ ຫຼື ຖັນທີ່ຊ້ຳກັນຫຼືບໍ່."

#. Khs7p
#: HandleDuplicateRecords.xhp
msgctxt ""
"HandleDuplicateRecords.xhp\n"
"par_id741725979527610\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Action:</emph> specifies whether to select or remove the duplicate rows or columns."
msgstr "<emph>ການດຳເນີນການ:</emph> ກຳນົດວ່າຈະເລືອກ ຫຼື ລຶບແຖວ ຫຼື ຖັນທີ່ຊ້ຳກັນ."

#. Wd2Av
#: HandleDuplicateRecords.xhp
msgctxt ""
"HandleDuplicateRecords.xhp\n"
"par_id781742303337461\n"
"help.text"
msgid "When duplicate records are removed, the entire rows or columns in the range containing those duplicates are deleted. This action causes the surrounding cells to shift and fill the empty spaces left behind. If the comparison is conducted along the rows, the cells below the removed duplicates will shift upward. Conversely, if the comparison is done along the columns, the cells to the right of the deleted duplicates will move leftward."
msgstr "ເມື່ອລຶບຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຊ້ຳກັນອອກ, ແຖວ ຫຼື ຖັນທັງໝົດໃນຊ່ວງທີ່ມີຂໍ້ມູນຊ້ຳນັ້ນຈະຖືກລຶບອອກ. ການດຳເນີນການນີ້ຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ເຊວທີ່ຢູ່ອ້ອມຂ້າງມີການຍັບຍ້າຍເພື່ອມາແທນທີ່ບ່ອນວ່າງ. ຫາກມີການປຽບທຽບຕາມແຖວ, ເເຊວທີ່ຢູ່ລຸ່ມຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຖືກລຶບຈະຍັບຂຶ້ນເທິງ. ໃນທາງກົງກັນຂ້າມ, ຫາກມີການປຽບທຽບຕາມຖັນ, ເຊວທີ່ຢູ່ເບື້ອງຂວາຂອງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຖືກລຶບຈະຍັບໄປທາງຊ້າຍ."

