"par_id240920171003293400\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\"><emph>Data Entry Form</emph> is a tool to make table data entry easy in spreadsheets.</ahelp> With the Data Entry Form, you can enter, edit and delete records (or rows) of data and avoid horizontal scrolling when the table has many columns or when some columns are very wide."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\"><emph>ແບບຟອມການປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນ</emph> ແມ່ນເຄື່ອງມືທີ່ຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ການປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນໃນຕາຕະລາງສະເປຣດຊີດງ່າຍຂຶ້ນ.</ahelp> ດ້ວຍແບບຟອມການປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນ, ທ່ານສາມາດປ້ອນ, ແກ້ໄຂ ແລະ ລຶບລະບຽບ (ຫຼື ແຖວ) ຂອງຂໍ້ມູນ ແລະ ຫຼີກລ່ຽງການເລື່ອນໜ້າຈໍໄປທາງຂວາງ ເມື່ອຕາຕະລາງມີຫຼາຍຖັນ ຫຼື ເມື່ອບາງຖັນມີຄວາມກວ້າງຫຼາຍ."

#. TxLvo
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"par_id731512558700034\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The form supports up to 32 columns."
msgstr "ແບບຟອມນີ້ຮອງຮັບໄດ້ສູງສຸດ 32 ຖັນ."

#. yiAjM
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"hd_id291512503277077\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Preparing the data entry form"
msgstr "ການກຽມແບບຟອມການປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນ"

#. BDary
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"par_id221512503284514\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To be effective, the Calc data table should have a header row, where each cell contents is the label of the column. The header cells contents become the label of each data field in the form."
msgstr "ເພື່ອໃຫ້ມີປະສິດທິພາບ, ຕາຕະລາງຂໍ້ມູນ Calc ຄວນຈະມີແຖວສ່ວນຫົວ, ໂດຍທີ່ເນື້ອໃນຂອງແຕ່ລະເຊວແມ່ນປ້າຍຊື່ຂອງຖັນ. ເນື້ອໃນຂອງເຊວສ່ວນຫົວຈະກາຍເປັນປ້າຍຊື່ຂອງແຕ່ລະເຂດຂໍ້ມູນໃນແບບຟອມ."

#. d9TGe
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"hd_id531512503300666\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Activating the form"
msgstr "ການເປີດໃຊ້ງານແບບຟອມ"

#. DG3DF
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"par_id551512503358101\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Place the cursor in the header row of the table."
msgstr "ວາງເຄີເຊີໄວ້ໃນແຖວສ່ວນຫົວຂອງຕາຕະລາງ."

#. F7HNg
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"par_id11512503369875\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <item type=\"menuitem\">Data - Form...</item>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <item type=\"menuitem\">ຂໍ້ມູນ - ແບບຟອມ...</item>."

#. qK3hk
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"hd_id361512503457039\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Filling the form with data"
msgstr "ການຕື່ມຂໍ້ມູນລົງໃນແບບຟອມ"

#. wE4Jo
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"par_id361512503457039\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Enter the data in the text fields. Press Enter or click <item type=\"literal\">New</item> to add it to the table."
msgstr "ປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນລົງໃນຊ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ. ກົດ Enter ຫຼື ຄລິກ <item type=\"literal\">ໃໝ່</item> ເພື່ອເພີ່ມມັນລົງໃນຕາຕະລາງ."

#. D5pB4
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"hd_id111512507319306\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Form dialog buttons"
msgstr "ປຸ່ມໄດອະນັອກຂອງຟອມ"

#. ZgLzp
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"par_id981512503964001\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>New</emph>: fill the record (table row cells) with the form fields contents and jump to the next record or add a new record in the bottom of the table."
msgstr "<emph>ໃໝ່</emph>: ປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນໃສ່ລະບຽບ (ຫ້ອງໃນແຖວຕາຕະລາງ) ດ້ວຍເນື້ອໃນຂອງຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນຟອມ ແລະ ໄປຫາລະບຽບຖັດໄປ ຫຼື ເພີ່ມລະບຽບໃໝ່ລົງທີ່ສ່ວນລຸ່ມຂອງຕາຕະລາງ."

#. ZEerU
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"par_id91512503864256\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Delete</emph>: deletes the current record."
msgstr "<emph>ລຶບ</emph>: ລຶບລະບຽບປັດຈຸບັນ."

#. zx2vB
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"par_id11512503887586\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Restore</emph>: when a form field is edited, restore the record contents to its initial state."
msgstr "<emph>ຄືນຄ່າ</emph>: ເມື່ອມີການແກ້ໄຂຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນຟອມ, ໃຫ້ຄືນຄ່າເນື້ອໃນຂອງລະບຽບໃຫ້ເປັນຄືກັບສະຖານະເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ."

#. hDmFK
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"par_id301512503881314\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Previous record</emph>: move to the previous record (table row)."
msgstr "<emph>ລະບຽບກ່ອນໜ້າ</emph>: ຍ້າຍໄປຫາລະບຽບກ່ອນໜ້າ (ແຖວຕາຕະລາງ)."

#. aMoBm
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"par_id51512503877397\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Next record</emph>: move to the next record."
msgstr "<emph>ລະບຽບຖັດໄປ</emph>: ຍ້າຍໄປຫາລະບຽບຖັດໄປ."

#. PEGis
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"par_id971512503871672\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Close</emph>: close the form."
msgstr "<emph>ປິດ</emph>: ປິດຟອມ."

#. LJADq
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"par_id951512509971073\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"media/helpimg/sc_data_form01.png\" id=\"img_id951512509971073\">            <alt id=\"alt_id951512509971073\">The form dialog box and header row cells as field labels</alt>        </image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"media/helpimg/sc_data_form01.png\" id=\"img_id951512509971073\">            <alt id=\"alt_id951512509971073\">ກ່ອງໄດອະນັອກຂອງຟອມ ແລະ ຫ້ອງໃນແຖວຫົວຂໍ້ເປັນປ້າຍຊື່ຊ່ອງຂໍ້ມູນ</alt>        </image>"

#. G3cSB
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"par_id351512558748321\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use the <item type=\"input\">Tab</item> and <item type=\"input\">Shift-Tab</item> keys to jump forth and back between text boxes of the form dialog."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ປຸ່ມ <item type=\"input\">Tab</item> ແລະ <item type=\"input\">Shift-Tab</item> ເພື່ອຍ້າຍໄປຂ້າງໜ້າ ແລະ ຍ້ອນກັບລະຫວ່າງກ່ອງຂໍ້ຄວາມຂອງໄດອະນັອກຟອມ."

#. QABKU
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"par_id731512558741034\n"
"help.text"
msgid "You can use the form scroll bar to move between records."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ແຖບເລື່ອນຂອງຟອມເພື່ອຍ້າຍລະຫວ່າງລະບຽບຕ່າງໆ."

#. tBjmH
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"hd_id701512558977465\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Reopening the form dialog"
msgstr "ການເປີດໄດອະນັອກຟອມຄືນໃໝ່"

#. CKgpJ
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"par_id181512558987528\n"
"help.text"
msgid "To reopen the form dialog, place the cursor on the header row and open the form. The displayed record in the form dialog is the first data record. Move to the last record before entering new data otherwise the current record will be edited."
msgstr "ເພື່ອເປີດໄດອະນັອກຟອມຄືນໃໝ່, ໃຫ້ວາງເຄີເຊີໄວ້ທີ່ແຖວຫົວຂໍ້ ແລ້ວເປີດຟອມ. ລະບຽບທີ່ສະແດງໃນໄດອະນັອກຟອມແມ່ນລະບຽບຂໍ້ມູນທຳອິດ. ໃຫ້ຍ້າຍໄປຫາລະບຽບສຸດທ້າຍກ່ອນທີ່ຈະປ້ອນຂໍ້ມູນໃໝ່, ຖ້າບໍ່ດັ່ງນັ້ນ ລະບຽບປັດຈຸບັນຈະຖືກແກ້ໄຂ."

#. 4mygu
#: data_form.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_form.xhp\n"
"par_id240920171007419799\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/shared/guide/data_forms.xhp\">Document Forms</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/shared/guide/data_forms.xhp\">ຟອມຂອງເອກະສານ</link>"

#. sATUB
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Data Provider for Spreadsheet"
msgstr "ຕົວສະໜອງຂໍ້ມູນສຳລັບແຜ່ນງານ"

#. VQBG3
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"bm_id240920171018528200\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>data provider;for spreadsheets</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>data provider;transformations</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>data provider;refresh data provider</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ຕົວສະໜອງຂໍ້ມູນ;ສຳລັບແຜ່ນງານ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຕົວສະໜອງຂໍ້ມູນ;ການແປງ</bookmark_value><bookmark_value>ຕົວສະໜອງຂໍ້ມູນ;ໂຫຼດຕົວສະໜອງຂໍ້ມູນຄືນໃໝ່</bookmark_value>"

#. LwDBX
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id240920171003006302\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"text/scalc/01/data_provider.xhp\">Data Provider for Spreadsheets</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"text/scalc/01/data_provider.xhp\">ຕົວສະໜອງຂໍ້ມູນສຳລັບແຜ່ນງານ</link>"

#. 6oyEp
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id240920171003293400\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Imports data from data sources. At present, the supported external data formats include CSV, HTML and XML files."
msgstr "ນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ມູນຈາກແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ. ໃນປັດຈຸບັນ, ຮູບແບບຂໍ້ມູນພາຍນອກທີ່ຮອງຮັບລວມມີໄຟລ໌ CSV, HTML ແລະ XML."

#. FTC4d
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id701739297912137\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Data may be imported from either local storage, such as CSV files, or from external sources, such as HTML Web Pages."
msgstr "ຂໍ້ມູນອາດຈະຖືກນຳເຂົ້າຈາກບ່ອນເກັບຂໍ້ມູນພາຍໃນ ເຊັ່ນ ໄຟລ໌ CSV ຫຼື ຈາກແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນພາຍນອກ ເຊັ່ນ ໜ້າເວັບ HTML."

#. ztpzA
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id211739297916678\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Additionally, data can be manipulated using various transformations before being loaded into the sheet."
msgstr "ນອກຈາກນັ້ນ, ຂໍ້ມູນສາມາດຖືກຈັດການໂດຍໃຊ້ການແປງຕ່າງໆ ກ່ອນທີ່ຈະຖືກໂຫຼດເຂົ້າໃນແຜ່ນງານ."

#. KWC3w
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id891739299423298\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <menuitem>Data - Data Provider</menuitem>."
msgstr "ເລືອກ <menuitem>ຂໍ້ມູນ - ຕົວສະໜອງຂໍ້ມູນ</menuitem>."

#. YVEro
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id521739272538944\n"
"help.text"
msgid "On the <menuitem>Data</menuitem> tab, choose <menuitem>Data Provider</menuitem>."
msgstr "ໃນແຖບ <menuitem>ຂໍ້ມູນ</menuitem>, ເລືອກ <menuitem>ຕົວສະໜອງຂໍ້ມູນ</menuitem>."

#. pui9X
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id771739306510904\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"cmd/lc_dataprovider.svg\" id=\"img_id461739306510904\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id521739306510904\">Icon Data Provider</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"cmd/lc_dataprovider.svg\" id=\"img_id461739306510904\" width=\"1cm\" height=\"1cm\"><alt id=\"alt_id521739306510904\">ໄອຄອນ ຕົວສະໜອງຂໍ້ມູນ</alt></image>"

#. PwGA8
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id851739306510904\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Data Provider"
msgstr "ຕົວສະໜອງຂໍ້ມູນ"

#. 46usF
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id41739294146861\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Database Range"
msgstr "ຊ່ວງຖານຂໍ້ມູນ"

#. xW85g
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id381739294159238\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The database range to receive the data from the provider. Choose the range from the available dropdown list."
msgstr "ຊ່ວງຖານຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຈະຮັບຂໍ້ມູນຈາກຕົວສະໜອງຂໍ້ມູນ. ເລືອກຊ່ວງຈາກລາຍການແບບເລື່ອນລົງທີ່ມີຢູ່."

#. MEmVh
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id11739294164013\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Data Format"
msgstr "ຮູບແບບຂໍ້ມູນ"

#. 8RSFJ
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id411739294172365\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The type of the data to be imported."
msgstr "ປະເພດຂອງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຈະນຳເຂົ້າ."

#. cVgmZ
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id771739294177396\n"
"help.text"
msgid "URL"
msgstr "URL"

#. maCTt
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id21739294199172\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The URL of the data provider. If the provider is a local file, insert the file path and name. If the provider is a web service, insert the URL."
msgstr "URL ຂອງຕົວສະໜອງຂໍ້ມູນ. ຖ້າຕົວສະໜອງຂໍ້ມູນແມ່ນໄຟລ໌ພາຍໃນ, ໃຫ້ໃສ່ເສັ້ນທາງໄຟລ໌ ແລະ ຊື່ໄຟລ໌. ຖ້າຕົວສະໜອງຂໍ້ມູນແມ່ນການບໍລິການເວັບ, ໃຫ້ໃສ່ URL."

#. AiBAv
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id881739294185949\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Identifier"
msgstr "ຕົວລະບຸ"

#. JpxVL
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id991739294192437\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The <emph>Xpath</emph> for XML or HTML provided data. For example, to get the fifth table of an HTML or XML document, the identifier must be <literal>//table[5]</literal>. The identifier <literal>//table</literal> is equivalent to <literal>//table[1]</literal>."
msgstr "<emph>Xpath</emph> ສຳລັບຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ສະໜອງໃຫ້ໃນຮູບແບບ XML ຫຼື HTML. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ເພື່ອດຶງເອົາຕາຕະລາງທີຫ້າຂອງເອກະສານ HTML ຫຼື XML, ຕົວລະບຸຕ້ອງແມ່ນ <literal>//table[5]</literal>. ຕົວລະບຸ <literal>//table</literal> ແມ່ນທຽບເທົ່າກັບ <literal>//table[1]</literal>."

#. e6EqK
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id81739294235914\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Transformations"
msgstr "ການແປງຂໍ້ມູນ"

#. dHLAf
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id131739297549651\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The provided data can be transformed using the available transformations from the dropdown list. You will need to provide further information depending on the transformation. For example, you can set the sort order for the sort transformations."
msgstr "ຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ສະໜອງໃຫ້ສາມາດຖືກແປງໂດຍໃຊ້ການແປງທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນລາຍການແບບເລື່ອນລົງ. ທ່ານຈະຕ້ອງໃຫ້ຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມຂຶ້ນກັບການແປງນັ້ນ. ຕົວຢ່າງ: ທ່ານສາມາດຕັ້ງລຳດັບການຮຽງລຳດັບສຳລັບການແປງແບບຮຽງລຳດັບ."

#. 6EBTB
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id121741205426373\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Delete Columns"
msgstr "ລຶບຖັນ"

#. GoEDC
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id371741264764548\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Deletes columns listed in <emph>Columns</emph>. Enter the list of columns indexes separated by semicolons."
msgstr "ລຶບຖັນທີ່ລະບຸໄວ້ໃນ <emph>ຖັນ</emph>. ປ້ອນລາຍການດັດສະນີຂອງຖັນໂດຍແຍກກັນດ້ວຍເຄື່ອງໝາຍຈ້ຳຈຸດ (;)."

#. BfcDM
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id21741205430956\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Delete Rows"
msgstr "ລຶບແຖວ"

#. NVwFS
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id351741264769117\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Deletes rows containing the value entered in <emph>Lookup value</emph> entry and found in <emph>Column</emph> index number."
msgstr "ລຶບແຖວທີ່ມີຄ່າທີ່ປ້ອນໃນ <emph>ຄ່າຄົ້ນຫາ</emph> ແລະ ພົບໃນເລກດັດສະນີຂອງ <emph>ຖັນ</emph>."

#. MZfRG
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id81741205435804\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Swap Rows"
msgstr "ສະລັບແຖວ"

#. tE432
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id491741264773681\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Swap row position between the first and second rows."
msgstr "ສະລັບຕຳແໜ່ງແຖວລະຫວ່າງແຖວທີໜຶ່ງ ແລະ ທີສອງ."

#. 3gdt7
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id891741205439580\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Split Columns"
msgstr "ແຍກຖັນ"

#. VD5ix
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id91741266520464\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Separates the column in two on the occurrence of the separator string."
msgstr "ແຍກຖັນອອກເປັນສອງສ່ວນເມື່ອພົບຂໍ້ຄວາມຕົວແຍກ."

#. qvYhx
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id801741205443572\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Merge Columns"
msgstr "ລວມຖັນ"

#. KJ7By
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id931741266512040\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Merges columns adding the separator string between each merged value."
msgstr "ລວມຖັນໂດຍການເພີ່ມຂໍ້ຄວາມຕົວແຍກລະຫວ່າງແຕ່ລະຄ່າທີ່ລວມກັນ."

#. DLYeb
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id781741205447620\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Text Transformation"
msgstr "ການແປງຂໍ້ຄວາມ"

#. pXuCw
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id251741287228280\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Transforms text data in the list of columns."
msgstr "ແປງຂໍ້ມູນຂໍ້ຄວາມໃນລາຍການຂອງຖັນ."

#. DqPGD
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id621741265182509\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>To Lower</emph>: transforms all uppercase characters to lowercase."
msgstr "<emph>ເປັນໂຕພິມນ້ອຍ</emph>: ແປງຕົວອັກສອນພິມໃຫຍ່ທັງໝົດໃຫ້ເປັນຕົວອັກສອນພິມນ້ອຍ."

#. CvJQk
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id931741266233821\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>To Upper</emph>: transforms all lowercase characters to uppercase."
msgstr "<emph>ເປັນໂຕພິມໃຫຍ່</emph>: ແປງຕົວອັກສອນພິມນ້ອຍທັງໝົດໃຫ້ເປັນຕົວອັກສອນພິມໃຫຍ່."

#. SbAQu
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id31741266350179\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Capitalize</emph>: capitalizes the first character of each word."
msgstr "<emph>ໂຕພິມໃຫຍ່ຂຶ້ນຕົ້ນ</emph>: ປ່ຽນຕົວອັກສອນທຳອິດຂອງແຕ່ລະຄຳໃຫ້ເປັນຕົວພິມໃຫຍ່."

#. eF6Br
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id811741266451457\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Trim</emph>: removes spaces from the data, leaving only a single space character between words."
msgstr "<emph>ຕັດຊ່ອງວ່າງ</emph>: ລຶບຊ່ອງວ່າງອອກຈາກຂໍ້ມູນ, ໂດຍເຫຼືອໄວ້ພຽງຊ່ອງວ່າງດຽວລະຫວ່າງຄຳ."

#. 2AUUt
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id591741205451860\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Sort Columns"
msgstr "ຮຽງລຳດັບຖັນ"

#. RAXov
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id541741268695831\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Sorts rows ascending or descending by the values in the column index number."
msgstr "ຮຽງລຳດັບແຖວຈາກນ້ອຍຫາໃຫຍ່ ຫຼື ຈາກໃຫຍ່ຫານ້ອຍ ຕາມຄ່າໃນເລກດັດສະນີຂອງຖັນ."

#. UFV9g
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id511741205455460\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Aggregate Functions"
msgstr "ຟັງຊັນການສັງລວມ"

#. Dzoej
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id271741269442206\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Adds the result of an aggregate function to the bottom of the column."
msgstr "ເພີ່ມຜົນຂອງຟັງຊັນການສັງລວມລົງທີ່ສ່ວນລຸ່ມຂອງຖັນ."

#. BWHTD
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id641741269370623\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Sum</emph>: the sum of the column data."
msgstr "<emph>ຜົນລວມ</emph>: ຜົນລວມຂອງຂໍ້ມູນໃນຖັນ."

#. CKH6k
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id751741269375319\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Average</emph>: the average value of the column data."
msgstr "<emph>ຄ່າສະເລ່ຍ</emph>: ຄ່າສະເລ່ຍຂອງຂໍ້ມູນໃນຖັນ."

#. zsm7B
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id211741269379607\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Maximum Value</emph>: the maximum value of the column data."
msgstr "<emph>ຄ່າສູງສຸດ</emph>: ຄ່າສູງສຸດຂອງຂໍ້ມູນໃນຖັນ."

#. yTJo6
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id271741269383551\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Minimum Value</emph>: the minimum value of the column data."
msgstr "<emph>ຄ່າຕ່ຳສຸດ</emph>: ຄ່າຕ່ຳສຸດຂອງຂໍ້ມູນໃນຖັນ."

#. 3242e
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id251741205460604\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Numeric"
msgstr "ຕົວເລກ"

#. HxbER
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id921741287284398\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Applies numeric functions on columns."
msgstr "ນຳໃຊ້ຟັງຊັນຕົວເລກກັບຖັນ."

#. CzfUM
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id181741286856945\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Sign</emph>: returns +1 for strictly positive numbers, -1 for strictly negative and 0 for zero values."
msgstr "<emph>ເຄື່ອງໝາຍ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າ +1 ສຳລັບເລກບວກ, -1 ສຳລັບເລກລົບ ແລະ 0 ສຳລັບຄ່າສູນ."

#. nV8jk
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id31741286861080\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Round</emph>: rounds numbers to a certain number of decimal places."
msgstr "<emph>ປັດເສດ</emph>: ປັດຕົວເລກໃຫ້ເປັນຈຳນວນຕຳແໜ່ງທົດສະນິຍົມທີ່ກຳນົດ."

#. F53YG
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id601741286864784\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Round Up</emph>: rounds numbers to the nearest upper integer."
msgstr "<emph>ປັດຂຶ້ນ</emph>: ປັດຕົວເລກໃຫ້ເປັນຈຳນວນຖ້ວນທີ່ສູງກວ່າທີ່ໃກ້ທີ່ສຸດ."

#. pYPxX
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id251741286868464\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Round Down</emph>: rounds numbers to the nearest lower integer."
msgstr "<emph>ປັດລົງ</emph>: ປັດຕົວເລກໃຫ້ເປັນຈຳນວນຖ້ວນທີ່ຕ່ຳກວ່າທີ່ໃກ້ທີ່ສຸດ."

#. kFnAs
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id571741286872864\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Absolute value</emph>: returns the absolute value of the numbers."
msgstr "<emph>ຄ່າສົມບູນ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າສົມບູນຂອງຕົວເລກ."

#. vLBin
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id761741286907711\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Log with base e</emph>: returns the natural logarithm of the numbers."
msgstr "<emph>Log ພື້ນ e</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າໂລກາຣິດທຳມະຊາດຂອງຕົວເລກ."

#. T4HbB
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id31741286926046\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Log with base 10</emph>: returns the logarithm base 10 of the numbers."
msgstr "<emph>Log ພື້ນ 10</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າໂລກາຣິດພື້ນ 10 ຂອງຕົວເລກ."

#. 7FAKL
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id641741286930767\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Cube</emph>: returns the cube of the numbers."
msgstr "<emph>ກຳລັງສາມ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າກຳລັງສາມຂອງຕົວເລກ."

#. bFyX7
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id251741286936459\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Square</emph>: returns the square of the numbers."
msgstr "<emph>ກຳລັງສອງ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າກຳລັງສອງຂອງຕົວເລກ."

#. xAGCv
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id431741286940734\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Square Root</emph>: returns the square root of the numbers."
msgstr "<emph>ຮາກຂັ້ນສອງ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າຮາກຂັ້ນສອງຂອງຕົວເລກ."

#. nbVD7
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id751741286945038\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Exponent</emph>: returns the exponential of the numbers (e<sup>x</sup>)."
msgstr "<emph>ເລກກຳລັງ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າເລກກຳລັງຂອງຕົວເລກ (e<sup>x</sup>)."

#. CCzMo
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id421741286949254\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Is Even</emph>: returns +1 is the number is even, 0 if the number is odd. Decimal numbers returns 0."
msgstr "<emph>ແມ່ນເລກຄູ່</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນ +1 ຖ້າຕົວເລກແມ່ນເລກຄູ່, 0 ຖ້າຕົວເລກແມ່ນເລກຄີກ. ຕົວເລກທົດສະນິຍົມຈະສົ່ງຄືນ 0."

#. FVcAR
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id851741286953094\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Is Odd</emph>: returns +1 is the number is odd, 0 if the number is even. Decimal numbers returns 0."
msgstr "<emph>ແມ່ນເລກຄີກ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນ +1 ຖ້າຕົວເລກແມ່ນເລກຄີກ, 0 ຖ້າຕົວເລກແມ່ນເລກຄູ່. ຕົວເລກທົດສະນິຍົມຈະສົ່ງຄືນ 0."

#. Rqpxa
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id151741205464747\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Replace Null"
msgstr "ແທນທີ່ຄ່າ Null (ຄ່າວ່າງ)"

#. FDHiB
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id171741287725956\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Replaces null or missing data in the list of columns with the supplied text."
msgstr "ແທນທີ່ຄ່າ Null ຫຼື ຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຂາດຫາຍໄປໃນລາຍການຖັນດ້ວຍຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ລະບຸ."

#. 5wVEA
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id891741205469100\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Date and Time"
msgstr "ວັນທີ ແລະ ເວລາ"

#. Ynns5
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id841741288387492\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Performs date and time transformations on data in the list of column indexes."
msgstr "ດຳເນີນການແປງວັນທີ ແລະ ເວລາກັບຂໍ້ມູນໃນລາຍການດັດສະນີຂອງຖັນ."

#. 9yQK6
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id761741295010729\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The date and time values depends on the locale settings."
msgstr "ຄ່າວັນທີ ແລະ ເວລາແມ່ນຂຶ້ນກັບການຕັ້ງຄ່າທ້ອງຖິ່ນ (Locale)."

#. WqkaF
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id721741290614073\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Date String</emph>:"
msgstr "<emph>ຂໍ້ຄວາມວັນທີ</emph>:"

#. v5GDK
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id731741290619260\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Year</emph>: returns the year of the date."
msgstr "<emph>ປີ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນປີຂອງວັນທີ."

#. FVjJv
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id601741290728493\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Start of Year</emph>: returns the date value of the first day of the year."
msgstr "<emph>ຕົ້ນປີ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າວັນທີຂອງມື້ທຳອິດຂອງປີ."

#. iQEzG
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id501741290733221\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>End of Year</emph>: returns the date value of the last day of the year."
msgstr "<emph>ທ້າຍປີ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າວັນທີຂອງມື້ສຸດທ້າຍຂອງປີ."

#. uGKwy
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id91741290737453\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Month</emph>: returns the month number of the date."
msgstr "<emph>ເດືອນ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນເລກເດືອນຂອງວັນທີ."

#. ngfFT
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id951741290741517\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Month Name</emph>: returns the month name of the date."
msgstr "<emph>ຊື່ເດືອນ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນຊື່ເດືອນຂອງວັນທີ."

#. pkydG
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id841741290745421\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Start of Month</emph>: returns the date value of first day of the month."
msgstr "<emph>ຕົ້ນເດືອນ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າວັນທີຂອງມື້ທຳອິດຂອງເດືອນ."

#. 6qJd8
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id511741290749881\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>End of Month</emph>: returns the date value of the last day of the month."
msgstr "<emph>ທ້າຍເດືອນ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າວັນທີຂອງມື້ສຸດທ້າຍຂອງເດືອນ."

#. EVWpj
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id351741290754069\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Day</emph>: returns the day of the month."
msgstr "<emph>ວັນ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນວັນຂອງເດືອນ."

#. G5jEt
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id511741290758021\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Day of Week</emph>: returns the day of the week."
msgstr "<emph>ວັນໃນອາທິດ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນວັນຂອງອາທິດ."

#. ckuXs
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id701741290761644\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Day of Year</emph>: returns the day of the year."
msgstr "<emph>ວັນໃນປີ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນວັນຂອງປີ."

#. nfYhS
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id881741290766989\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Quarter</emph>: returns the quarter number of the date."
msgstr "<emph>ໄຕມາດ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນເລກໄຕມາດຂອງວັນທີ."

#. ecsAP
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id531741290770820\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Start of Quarter</emph>: returns the date value of the first day of the quarter."
msgstr "<emph>ຕົ້ນໄຕມາດ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າວັນທີຂອງມື້ທຳອິດຂອງໄຕມາດ."

#. GBoLY
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id631741290775108\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>End of Quarter</emph>: returns the date value of the last day of the quarter."
msgstr "<emph>ທ້າຍໄຕມາດ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າວັນທີຂອງມື້ສຸດທ້າຍຂອງໄຕມາດ."

#. jhPCC
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id511741290839522\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Hour</emph>: returns the hour of the date."
msgstr "<emph>ຊົ່ວໂມງ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນຊົ່ວໂມງຂອງວັນທີ."

#. R5BYG
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id961741290843338\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Minute</emph>: returns the minute of the date."
msgstr "<emph>ນາທີ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນນາທີຂອງວັນທີ."

#. fdSwy
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id291741290847683\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Second</emph>: returns the second of the date."
msgstr "<emph>ວິນາທີ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນວິນາທີຂອງວັນທີ."

#. fVaV7
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id731741290851850\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Time</emph>: returns the time of the date."
msgstr "<emph>ເວລາ</emph>: ສົ່ງຄືນເວລາຂອງວັນທີ."

#. tZPUD
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id431741205473092\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Find and Replace"
msgstr "ຊອກຫາ ແລະ ແທນທີ່"

#. sGFbH
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id11741291871906\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Finds and replaces values in <emph>Column</emph> index number."
msgstr "ຊອກຫາ ແລະ ແທນທີ່ຄ່າໃນເລກດັດສະນີຂອງ <emph>ຖັນ</emph>."

#. 6QDUr
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id341739296057828\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Add"
msgstr "ເພີ່ມ"

#. EwA7s
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id871739296067246\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click <emph>Add</emph> to include the selected transformation to the transformation set. Transformations are included at the bottom of the list."
msgstr "ຄລິກ <emph>ເພີ່ມ</emph> ເພື່ອລວມເອົາການແປງທີ່ເລືອກເຂົ້າໃນຊຸດການແປງ. ການແປງຈະຖືກເພີ່ມເຂົ້າທີ່ສ່ວນລຸ່ມຂອງລາຍການ."

#. 4UxBs
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id611739296048750\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If the order of transformations is important, plan the sequence of transformations in advance."
msgstr "ຖ້າລຳດັບຂອງການແປງມີຄວາມສຳຄັນ, ໃຫ້ວາງແຜນລຳດັບການແປງໄວ້ລ່ວງໜ້າ."

#. omwig
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id1001739297490451\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Delete"
msgstr "ລຶບ"

#. mFFea
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id81739297506339\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Deletes the transformation from the list."
msgstr "ລຶບການແປງອອກຈາກລາຍການ."

#. NEDh7
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"hd_id751739298168981\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Apply"
msgstr "ນຳໃຊ້"

#. 3En6Q
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id171739298177326\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Applies the transformations to the provided data and displays results in the preview area for inspection. The data is not loaded in the spreadsheet until you press <emph>OK</emph>."
msgstr "ນຳໃຊ້ການແປງກັບຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ສະໜອງໃຫ້ ແລະ ສະແດງຜົນໃນພື້ນທີ່ສະແດງຕົວຢ່າງເພື່ອໃຫ້ກວດສອບ. ຂໍ້ມູນຈະຍັງບໍ່ຖືກໂຫຼດເຂົ້າໃນແຜ່ນງານຈົນກວ່າທ່ານຈະກົດ <emph>ຕົກລົງ</emph>."

#. XLXhu
#: data_provider.xhp
msgctxt ""
"data_provider.xhp\n"
"par_id131741901871041\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The data formatting can be set with a right-click on the preview table column headers. The corresponding database range column is then selected. Format the cells with the context menu."
msgstr "ການຈັດຮູບແບບຂໍ້ມູນສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າໄດ້ໂດຍການຄລິກຂວາໃສ່ສ່ວນຫົວຖັນຂອງຕາຕະລາງສະແດງຕົວຢ່າງ. ຈາກນັ້ນຖັນຊ່ວງຖານຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງຈະຖືກເລືອກ. ຈັດຮູບແບບຫ້ອງດ້ວຍເມນູບໍລິບົດ."

