#. CATpt
#: formula2value.xhp
msgctxt ""
"formula2value.xhp\n"
"par_id501645222861116\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Replaces the formula cell with value calculated by the formula. The formula is lost."
msgstr "ແທນທີ່ຫ້ອງທີ່ມີສູດດ້ວຍຄ່າທີ່ຄຳນວນໄດ້ຈາກສູດນັ້ນ. ສູດຈະຖືກລຶບອອກ."

#. AKrcm
#: formula2value.xhp
msgctxt ""
"formula2value.xhp\n"
"par_id51645230882532\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use this command to convert formula cells into data cells. The converted cells contents becomes static and will not be recalculated."
msgstr "ໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງນີ້ເພື່ອແປງຫ້ອງສູດໃຫ້ເປັນຫ້ອງຂໍ້ມູນ. ເນື້ອໃນຂອງຫ້ອງທີ່ແປງແລ້ວຈະຄົງທີ່ ແລະ ຈະບໍ່ຖືກຄຳນວນຄືນໃໝ່."

#. 6LMA9
#: ful_func.xhp
msgctxt ""
"ful_func.xhp\n"
"par_id631683055048736\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Microsoft Excel <link href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-US/office/troubleshoot/excel/wrongly-assumes-1900-is-leap-year\">wrongly assumes year 1900 to be a leap year</link> and considers the inexistent day of 1900-02-29 as valid in date calculations. Dates prior to 1900-03-01 are therefore different in Excel and Calc."
msgstr "Microsoft Excel <link href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-US/office/troubleshoot/excel/wrongly-assumes-1900-is-leap-year\">ສົມມຸດຜິດວ່າປີ 1900 ເປັນປີອະທິກະສຸຣະທິນ (Leap year)</link> ແລະ ຖືວ່າມື້ທີ່ບໍ່ມີຕົວຈິງຄື 1900-02-29 ເປັນມື້ທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງໃນການຄຳນວນວັນທີ. ດັ່ງນັ້ນ, ວັນທີກ່ອນ 1900-03-01 ຈຶ່ງແຕກຕ່າງກັນໃນ Excel ແລະ Calc."

