msgid "<variable id=\"variable name\"><ahelp hid=\".\">Returns the starting position of a given text, using byte positions. FINDB is case sensitive.</ahelp></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"variable name\"><ahelp hid=\".\">ສົ່ງຄືນຕຳແໜ່ງເລີ່ມຕົ້ນຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ກຳນົດ ໂດຍໃຊ້ຕຳແໜ່ງໄບຕ໌ (byte). FINDB ຈະແຍກຕົວອັກສອນນ້ອຍ-ໃຫຍ່.</ahelp></variable>"

