#. okEBS
#: func_findb.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_findb.xhp\n"
"par_id481573517830373\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<input>=FINDB(\"ａ\"; \"LibreOffice Ｃａｌｃ\")</input> returns 15. The <emph>Find Text</emph> argument is a text string that comprises a full-width, double-byte \"a\" character, while the <emph>Text</emph> argument comprises 12 single-byte characters followed by four full-width, double-byte characters."
msgstr "<input>=FINDB(\"ａ\"; \"LibreOffice Ｃａｌｃ\")</input> ສົ່ງຄືນ 15. ອາກິວເມັນ <emph>ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຈະຄົ້ນຫາ</emph> ແມ່ນຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ມີຕົວອັກສອນ \"a\" ແບບ double-byte (full-width), ໃນຂະນະທີ່ອາກິວເມັນ <emph>ຂໍ້ຄວາມ</emph> ປະກອບດ້ວຍຕົວອັກສອນ single-byte 12 ຕົວ ຕາມດ້ວຍຕົວອັກສອນ double-byte (full-width) 4 ຕົວ."

