#. fEf7M
#: func_forecastetsstatmult.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_forecastetsstatmult.xhp\n"
"hd_id040312316112394554\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Returns 15.8372533480997, the multiplicative statistics based on <emph>Values</emph> and <emph>Timeline</emph> named ranges above, with root mean squared error, no missing data, and SUM as aggregation."
msgstr "ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າ 15.8372533480997, ເຊິ່ງແມ່ນສະຖິຕິແບບທະວີຄູນໂດຍອີງຕາມຊ່ວງທີ່ຕັ້ງຊື່ໄວ້ <emph>Values</emph> ແລະ <emph>Timeline</emph> ຂ້າງເທິງ, ດ້ວຍຄ່າຜິດພາດກຳລັງສອງສະເລ່ຍ (root mean squared error), ບໍ່ມີຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຂາດຫາຍ, ແລະ ໃຊ້ SUM ເປັນການລວບລວມຂໍ້ມູນ."

