#. 8sMKs
#: func_ifs.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_ifs.xhp\n"
"par_id181556235788473\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If expression is neither TRUE or FALSE, a #VALUE error is returned."
msgstr "ຖ້ານິພົດບໍ່ແມ່ນທັງ TRUE ຫຼື FALSE, ຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ #VALUE ຈະຖືກສົ່ງຄືນ."

