msgctxt ""
"func_lenb.xhp\n"
"par_id2956018\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<item type=\"input\">LENB(\"中\")</item> returns 2 (1 DBCS character consisting of 2 bytes)."
msgstr "<item type=\"input\">LENB(\"中\")</item> ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າ 2 (1 ຕົວອັກສອນ DBCS ເຊິ່ງປະກອບດ້ວຍ 2 ໄບຕ໌)."

#. LGCLu
#: func_lenb.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_lenb.xhp\n"
"par_id2956028\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<item type=\"input\">LENB(\"中国\")</item> returns 4 (2 DBCS characters each consisting of 2 bytes)."
msgstr "<item type=\"input\">LENB(\"中国\")</item> ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າ 4 (2 ຕົວອັກສອນ DBCS ເຊິ່ງແຕ່ລະຕົວປະກອບດ້ວຍ 2 ໄບຕ໌)."

#. oEBva
#: func_lenb.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_lenb.xhp\n"
"par_id2956038\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<item type=\"input\">LENB(\"office\")</item> returns 6 (6 non-DBCS characters each consisting of 1 byte)."
msgstr "<item type=\"input\">LENB(\"office\")</item> ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າ 6 (6 ຕົວອັກສອນທີ່ບໍ່ແມ່ນ DBCS ເຊິ່ງແຕ່ລະຕົວມີຂະໜາດ 1 ໄບຕ໌)."

#. BNVMh
#: func_lenb.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_lenb.xhp\n"
"par_id2956008\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<item type=\"input\">=LENB(\"Good Afternoon\")</item> returns 14."
msgstr "<item type=\"input\">=LENB(\"Good Afternoon\")</item> ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າ 14."

#. 7bZu3
#: func_lenb.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_lenb.xhp\n"
"par_id2954300\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<item type=\"input\">=LENB(12345.67)</item> returns 8."
msgstr "<item type=\"input\">=LENB(12345.67)</item> ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າ 8."

#. MfDYe
#: func_lenb.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_lenb.xhp\n"
"par_id71677014897959\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"https://wiki.documentfoundation.org/Documentation/Calc_Functions/LENB\">LENB wiki page</link>."
msgstr "<link href=\"https://wiki.documentfoundation.org/Documentation/Calc_Functions/LENB\">ໜ້າວິິກິ LENB</link>."

#. ANivD
#: func_let.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_let.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "LET function"
msgstr "ຟັງຊັນ LET"

#. mp4Fy
#: func_let.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_let.xhp\n"
"bm_id361708283183878\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>LET function</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ຟັງຊັນ LET</bookmark_value>"

#. cUrJc
#: func_let.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_let.xhp\n"
"hd_id721717677746932\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"h1\"><link href=\"text/scalc/01/func_let.xhp\">LET</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"h1\"><link href=\"text/scalc/01/func_let.xhp\">LET</link></variable>"

#. NFFDr
#: func_let.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_let.xhp\n"
"par_id71717677746935\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Assigns names to calculation results. This allows storing intermediate calculations, values, or defining names inside a formula. These names only apply within the scope of the LET function."
msgstr "ກຳນົດຊື່ໃຫ້ກັບຜົນການຄຳນວນ. ສິ່ງນີ້ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ສາມາດເກັບຄ່າການຄຳນວນລະຫວ່າງກາງ, ຄ່າຕ່າງໆ ຫຼື ກຳນົດຊື່ພາຍໃນສູດໄດ້. ຊື່ເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຈະມີຜົນໃຊ້ສະເພາະພາຍໃນຂອບເຂດຂອງຟັງຊັນ LET ເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#. nxYmy
#: func_let.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_let.xhp\n"
"par_id211708281649651\n"
"help.text"
msgid "=LET(Name1; Name_value1; Calculation_or_Name2 [; Name_value2; Calculation_or_Name3 [; ...]])"
msgstr "=LET(Name1; Name_value1; Calculation_or_Name2 [; Name_value2; Calculation_or_Name3 [; ...]])"

#. voGvK
#: func_let.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_let.xhp\n"
"par_id301717681619674\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Name1</emph>: the first name to assign. Must start with a letter. Cannot be the output of a formula or conflict with range syntax."
msgstr "<emph>Name1</emph>: ຊື່ທຳອິດທີ່ຈະກຳນົດ. ຕ້ອງເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍຕົວອັກສອນ. ບໍ່ສາມາດເປັນຜົນລັດຂອງສູດ ຫຼື ຂັດກັບໄວຍາກອນຂອງຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນ."

#. CDP5D
#: func_let.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_let.xhp\n"
"par_id721717688901981\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Name1 must follow the <link href=\"text/scalc/guide/value_with_name.xhp\">naming rules of %PRODUCTNAME Calc</link>."
msgstr "Name1 ຕ້ອງປະຕິບັດຕາມ <link href=\"text/scalc/guide/value_with_name.xhp\">ກົດລະບຽບການຕັ້ງຊື່ຂອງ %PRODUCTNAME Calc</link>."

#. pXGwN
#: func_let.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_let.xhp\n"
"par_id951717681624139\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Name_value1</emph>: the value or calculation to assign to Name1."
msgstr "<emph>Name_value1</emph>: ຄ່າ ຫຼື ການຄຳນວນທີ່ຈະກຳນົດໃຫ້ກັບ Name1."

#. RpF5L
#: func_let.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_let.xhp\n"
"par_id421717686226452\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Name2; Name_value2;...</emph>: (optional) same as Name1 and Name_value1, respectively. Name_value2 must follow Name2 and so on."
msgstr "<emph>Name2; Name_value2;...</emph>: (ທາງເລືອກ) ຄືກັນກັບ Name1 ແລະ Name_value1 ຕາມລຳດັບ. Name_value2 ຕ້ອງຕາມຫຼັງ Name2 ໄປເລື້ອຍໆ."

#. ii4Cd
#: func_let.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_let.xhp\n"
"par_id231717686233659\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Calculation</emph>: a formula expression that uses all names within the LET function."
msgstr "<emph>Calculation</emph>: ນິພົດຂອງສູດທີ່ໃຊ້ຊື່ທັງໝົດທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ພາຍໃນຟັງຊັນ LET."

#. AaFRL
#: func_let.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_let.xhp\n"
"par_id91717686350018\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Calculation</emph> must be the last argument in the LET function."
msgstr "<emph>Calculation</emph> ຕ້ອງເປັນຕົວໂຕ້ແຍ້ງສຸດທ້າຍໃນຟັງຊັນ LET."

#. vGdpF
#: func_let.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_let.xhp\n"
"par_id121717701196975\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Calculate the molar mass of the water molecule knowing that the molecule has 2 hydrogen atoms and one oxygen atom."
msgstr "ຄຳນວນມວນໂມເລກຸນຂອງນ້ຳ ໂດຍຮູ້ວ່າໂມເລກຸນມີອາໂຕມຮີໂດຣແຊນ 2 ອາໂຕມ ແລະ ອາໂຕມອົກຊີແຊນ 1 ອາໂຕມ."

#. s46BC
#: func_let.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_let.xhp\n"
"par_id311717701158800\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<input>=LET(mHydro; HLOOKUP(\"Hydrogen\"; $A$1:$DO$4; 4; 0); mOxy; HLOOKUP(\"Oxygen\"; $A$1:$DO$4; 4; 0); \"The molar mass of water is \"&(mOxy+2*mHydro)&\" g/mol\")</input> returns \"The molar mass of water is 18.015 g/mol\"."
msgstr "<input>=LET(mHydro; HLOOKUP(\"Hydrogen\"; $A$1:$DO$4; 4; 0); mOxy; HLOOKUP(\"Oxygen\"; $A$1:$DO$4; 4; 0); \"ມວນໂມເລກຸນຂອງນ້ຳແມ່ນ \"&(mOxy+2*mHydro)&\" g/mol\")</input> ສົ່ງຄືນ \"ມວນໂມເລກຸນຂອງນ້ຳແມ່ນ 18.015 g/mol\"."

#. TGwea
#: func_let.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_let.xhp\n"
"par_id701677016751508\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"https://wiki.documentfoundation.org/Documentation/Calc_Functions/LET\">LET wiki page</link>."
msgstr "<link href=\"https://wiki.documentfoundation.org/Documentation/Calc_Functions/LET\">ໜ້າວິິກິ LET</link>."

#. a9aTP
#: func_lookup.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_lookup.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Function LOOKUP"
msgstr "ຟັງຊັນ LOOKUP"

#. DBqzN
#: func_lookup.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_lookup.xhp\n"
"bm_id3159273\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>LOOKUP function</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ຟັງຊັນ LOOKUP</bookmark_value>"

#. 4G3NM
#: func_lookup.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_lookup.xhp\n"
"hd_id521750255960624\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"h1\"><link href=\"text/scalc/01/func_lookup.xhp\">LOOKUP</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"h1\"><link href=\"text/scalc/01/func_lookup.xhp\">LOOKUP</link></variable>"

#. cABv2
#: func_lookup.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_lookup.xhp\n"
"par_id3153389\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FUNC_VERWEIS\">Look for criterion in an already-sorted array, and return a corresponding result. Returns the contents of a cell either from a one-row or one-column range.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FUNC_VERWEIS\">ຄົ້ນຫາເກນໃນອາເຣທີ່ໄດ້ຈັດລຽງລຳດັບໄວ້ແລ້ວ ແລະ ສົ່ງຄືນຜົນລັດທີ່ກົງກັນ. ສົ່ງຄືນເນື້ອໃນຂອງເຊວຈາກຊ່ວງທີ່ມີແຖວດຽວ ຫຼື ຄໍລຳດຽວ.</ahelp>"

#. 4LY9p
#: func_lookup.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_lookup.xhp\n"
"par_id841750257069690\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Optionally, the assigned value (of the same index) is returned in a different column and row. As opposed to <link href=\"text/scalc/01/04060109.xhp#Section9\">VLOOKUP</link> and <link href=\"text/scalc/01/04060109.xhp#Section17\">HLOOKUP</link>, search and result vector may be at different positions; they do not have to be adjacent."
msgstr "ທາງເລືອກອື່ນ, ຄ່າທີ່ກຳນົດໃຫ້ (ທີ່ມີດັດຊະນີດຽວກັນ) ຈະຖືກສົ່ງຄືນໃນຄໍລຳ ແລະ ແຖວທີ່ຕ່າງກັນ. ເຊິ່ງຕ່າງຈາກ <link href=\"text/scalc/01/04060109.xhp#Section9\">VLOOKUP</link> ແລະ <link href=\"text/scalc/01/04060109.xhp#Section17\">HLOOKUP</link>, ເພາະຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຄົ້ນຫາ ແລະ ຊ່ວງຜົນລັດອາດຈະຢູ່ຕຳແໜ່ງທີ່ຕ່າງກັນ; ບໍ່ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງຢູ່ຕິດກັນ."

#. FFnAd
#: func_lookup.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_lookup.xhp\n"
"par_id3154104\n"
"help.text"
msgid "LOOKUP(Lookup; SearchVector [; ResultVector])"
msgstr "LOOKUP(Lookup; SearchVector [; ResultVector])"

#. AmM3v
#: func_lookup.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_lookup.xhp\n"
"par_id3150646\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Lookup</emph> is the value of any type to be looked for; entered either directly or as a reference."
msgstr "<emph>Lookup</emph> ແມ່ນຄ່າຂອງປະເພດຂໍ້ມູນໃດໆ ທີ່ຕ້ອງການຄົ້ນຫາ; ສາມາດປ້ອນໂດຍກົງ ຫຼື ເປັນການອ້າງອີງເຊວ."

#. teRj8
#: func_lookup.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_lookup.xhp\n"
"par_id3154854\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>SearchVector</emph> is an array of data. The lookup is performed in the  first row or first column of the array."
msgstr "<emph>SearchVector</emph> ແມ່ນອາເຣຂອງຂໍ້ມູນ. ການຄົ້ນຫາຈະຖືກປະຕິບັດໃນແຖວທຳອິດ ຫຼື ຄໍລຳທຳອິດຂອງອາເຣ."

#. GCzPH
#: func_lookup.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_lookup.xhp\n"
"par_id591750269646975\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The search vector for the LOOKUP must be sorted ascending, otherwise the search will not return any usable results. Numerical values precede values of type Text if both types are included (for example, -2, 0, 2, “A”, “B”)."
msgstr "ຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນຄົ້ນຫາ (Search vector) ສຳລັບ LOOKUP ຕ້ອງຖືກຈັດລຽງລຳດັບຈາກນ້ອຍຫາໃຫຍ່, ຖ້າບໍ່ດັ່ງນັ້ນການຄົ້ນຫາຈະບໍ່ສົ່ງຄືນຜົນລັດທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ. ຄ່າຕົວເລກຈະມາກ່ອນຄ່າປະເພດຂໍ້ຄວາມ ຖ້າມີທັງສອງປະເພດຢູ່ຮ່ວມກັນ (ຕົວຢ່າງ: -2, 0, 2, “A”, “B”)."

#. wZV9r
#: func_lookup.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_lookup.xhp\n"
"par_id841750275617013\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If <emph>SearchVector</emph> has same number of columns and rows or has more rows than columns, LOOKUP searches in the first column (similar to VLOOKUP), and returns the corresponding value in the last column."
msgstr "ຖ້າ <emph>SearchVector</emph> ມີຈຳນວນຄໍລຳ ແລະ ແຖວເທົ່າກັນ ຫຼື ມີຈຳນວນແຖວຫຼາຍກວ່າຄໍລຳ, LOOKUP ຈະຄົ້ນຫາໃນຄໍລຳທຳອິດ (ຄືກັບ VLOOKUP), ແລະ ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າທີ່ກົງກັນໃນຄໍລຳສຸດທ້າຍ."

#. KpDka
#: func_lookup.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_lookup.xhp\n"
"par_id311750275609300\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If <emph>SearchVector</emph> has more columns than rows, LOOKUP searches in the first row (similar to HLOOKUP), and returns the corresponding value in the last row."
msgstr "ຖ້າ <emph>SearchVector</emph> ມີຈຳນວນຄໍລຳຫຼາຍກວ່າແຖວ, LOOKUP ຈະຄົ້ນຫາໃນແຖວທຳອິດ (ຄືກັບ HLOOKUP), ແລະ ສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າທີ່ກົງກັນໃນແຖວສຸດທ້າຍ."

#. SkQoD
#: func_lookup.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_lookup.xhp\n"
"par_id3149925\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>ResultVector</emph> is another single-row or single-column range from which the result of the function is taken. The result is the cell of the result vector with the same index as the instance found in the search vector."
msgstr "<emph>ResultVector</emph> ແມ່ນອີກຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນໜຶ່ງທີ່ມີແຖວດຽວ ຫຼື ຄໍລຳດຽວ ເຊິ່ງຈະເປັນບ່ອນດຶງເອົາຜົນລັດຂອງຟັງຊັນ. ຜົນລັດທີ່ໄດ້ແມ່ນຄ່າໃນເຊວຂອງຊ່ວງຜົນລັດທີ່ມີດັດຊະນີດຽວກັນກັບຕຳແໜ່ງທີ່ພົບໃນຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນຄົ້ນຫາ."

#. yyJoV
#: func_lookup.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_lookup.xhp\n"
"par_id771750268996719\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If <emph>ResultVector</emph> is omitted, the function returns the value found in the last row or last column of the <emph>SearchVector</emph> array."
msgstr "ຖ້າບໍ່ມີການລະບຸ <emph>ResultVector</emph>, ຟັງຊັນຈະສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າທີ່ພົບໃນແຖວສຸດທ້າຍ ຫຼື ຄໍລຳສຸດທ້າຍຂອງອາເຣ <emph>SearchVector</emph>."

#. UzAZX
#: func_lookup.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_lookup.xhp\n"
"par_id991750269088955\n"
"help.text"
msgid "If <emph>SearchVector</emph> is a one-dimensional array and if <emph>ResultVector</emph> is omitted, the function returns the last occurrence of the lookup value if it exists in the <emph>SearchVector</emph>."
msgstr "ຖ້າ <emph>SearchVector</emph> ເປັນອາເຣມິຕິດຽວ ແລະ ບໍ່ໄດ້ລະບຸ <emph>ResultVector</emph>, ຟັງຊັນຈະສົ່ງຄືນຄ່າສຸດທ້າຍທີ່ພົບຂອງຄ່າທີ່ຄົ້ນຫາ ຖ້າມັນມີຢູ່ໃນ <emph>SearchVector</emph>."

