"par_id3148820\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Text</emph> is the text containing the characters to extract."
msgstr "<emph>Text</emph> ແມ່ນຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ບັນຈຸຕົວອັກສອນທີ່ຕ້ອງການດຶງອອກມາ."

#. qQkwz
