#. wiB9R
#: func_right.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_right.xhp\n"
"par_id3149426\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Text</emph> is the text of which the right part is to be determined."
msgstr "<emph>ຂໍ້ຄວາມ</emph> ແມ່ນຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຕ້ອງການດຶງເອົາສ່ວນເບື້ອງຂວາ."

#. z5Uwk
#: func_right.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_right.xhp\n"
"par_id3153350\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>Number</emph> (optional) is the number of characters from the right part of the text. If this parameter is not defined, one character is returned."
msgstr "<emph>ຈຳນວນ</emph> (ທາງເລືອກ) ແມ່ນຈຳນວນຕົວອັກສອນຈາກສ່ວນເບື້ອງຂວາຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ. ຖ້າບໍ່ໄດ້ກຳນົດພາລາມິເຕີນີ້, ຈະສົ່ງຄືນຕົວອັກສອນດຽວ."

#. od2ta
