"par_id2945375\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FUNC_RIGHTB\">Returns the last character or characters of a text with double bytes characters sets (DBCS).</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FUNC_RIGHTB\">ສົ່ງຄືນຕົວອັກສອນສຸດທ້າຍ ຫຼື ຫຼາຍຕົວອັກສອນສຸດທ້າຍຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ມີຊຸດຕົວອັກສອນແບບສອງໄບຕ໌ (DBCS).</ahelp>"

