#. eB2A7
#: func_unique.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_unique.xhp\n"
"par_id801715981230387\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<input>{=UNIQUE(B1:C10; FALSE(); TRUE())}</input>, with <emph>Uniqueness</emph> as TRUE. Returns the array below with the rows of Andy, Harry, Eva and Irene omitted because their combined grades and ages are not unique."
msgstr "<input>{=UNIQUE(B1:C10; FALSE(); TRUE())}</input>, ໂດຍທີ່ <emph>Uniqueness</emph> ເປັນ TRUE. ຈະສົ່ງຄືນອາເຣດ້ານລຸ່ມໂດຍຂ້າມແຖວຂອງ Andy, Harry, Eva ແລະ Irene ເພາະວ່າຄະແນນ ແລະ ອາຍຸ ທີ່ລວມກັນນັ້ນມີຄ່າຊ້ຳກັນ."

