#. mcyKX
#: func_weekday.xhp
msgctxt ""
"func_weekday.xhp\n"
"par_id3154228\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FUNC_WOCHENTAG\">Returns the day of the week for the given date value.</ahelp> The day is returned as an integer between 1 (Sunday) and 7 (Saturday) if no type or type=1 is specified. For other types, see the table below."
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\"HID_FUNC_WOCHENTAG\">ສົ່ງຄືນວັນໃນຮອບສັບດາ ສຳລັບຄ່າວັນທີທີ່ກຳນົດ.</ahelp> ວັນຈະຖືກສົ່ງຄືນເປັນເລກຖ້ວນລະຫວ່າງ 1 (ວັນອາທິດ) ຫາ 7 (ວັນເສົາ) ຖ້າບໍ່ໄດ້ລະບຸປະເພດ ຫຼື ລະບຸ type=1. ສຳລັບປະເພດອື່ນໆ, ໃຫ້ເບິ່ງຕາຕະລາງດ້ານລຸ່ມ."

#. SaqiJ
#: func_weekday.xhp
msgctxt ""
