msgstr "<input>{=XLOOKUP(\"Kryptonite\";B1:DO1;B1:DO4;\"Unknown element\")}</input> ສົ່ງຄືນອາເຣ {\"Unknown element\",\"Unknown element\",\"Unknown element\",\"Unknown element\"}."

