"par_id111708281542144\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<emph>0</emph>: exact match (default). If <emph>Search criterion</emph> value is not found, then return the #N/A error."
msgstr "<emph>0</emph>: ຈັບຄູ່ແບບແນ່ນອນ (ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ). ຫາກບໍ່ພົບຄ່າ <emph>Search criterion</emph>, ໃຫ້ສົ່ງຄືນຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ #N/A."

#. tCBq9
#: func_xmatch.xhp
