"help.text"
msgid "ANOVA is the acronym for <emph>AN</emph>alysis <emph>O</emph>f <emph>VA</emph>riance. This tool produces the analysis of variance of a given data set"
msgstr "ANOVA ແມ່ນຕົວອັກສອນຫຍໍ້ຂອງ <emph>AN</emph>alysis <emph>O</emph>f <emph>VA</emph>riance. ເຄື່ອງມືນີ້ສ້າງການວິເຄາະຄວາມຜັນປ່ຽນຂອງຊຸດຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ກຳນົດໃຫ້"

