#. 85aLv
#: statistics_correlation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"statistics_correlation.xhp\n"
"par_id1001760\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The correlation coefficient (a value between -1 and +1) means how strongly two variables are related to each other. You can use the CORREL function or the Data Statistics to find the correlation coefficient between two variables."
msgstr "ສຳປະສິດສະຫະສຳພັນ (ຄ່າລະຫວ່າງ -1 ຫາ +1) ໝາຍເຖິງລະດັບຄວາມກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັນຂອງສອງຕົວປ່ຽນ. ທ່ານສາມາດໃຊ້ຟັງຊັນ CORREL ຫຼື ສະຖິຕິຂໍ້ມູນເພື່ອຫາສຳປະສິດສະຫະສຳພັນລະຫວ່າງສອງຕົວປ່ຽນ."

#. Az6pZ
#: statistics_correlation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"statistics_correlation.xhp\n"
"par_id1001770\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A correlation coefficient of +1 indicates a perfect positive correlation."
msgstr "ສຳປະສິດສະຫະສຳພັນທີ່ເປັນ +1 ບົ່ງບອກເຖິງສະຫະສຳພັນທາງບວກທີ່ສົມບູນ."

#. FtKmy
#: statistics_correlation.xhp
msgctxt ""
"statistics_correlation.xhp\n"
"par_id1001780\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A correlation coefficient of -1 indicates a perfect negative correlation"
msgstr "ສຳປະສິດສະຫະສຳພັນທີ່ເປັນ -1 ບົ່ງບອກເຖິງສະຫະສຳພັນທາງລົບທີ່ສົມບູນ"

