"hd_id240920171003006302\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"h1\"><link href=\"text/scalc/01/xml_source.xhp\">XML Source</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"h1\"><link href=\"text/scalc/01/xml_source.xhp\">ແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ XML</link></variable>"

#. Fk6c7
#: xml_source.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xml_source.xhp\n"
"par_id240920171003293400\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<ahelp hid=\".\">Import XML data from arbitrarily structured XML content into cells in an existing spreadsheet document.</ahelp>"
msgstr "<ahelp hid=\".\">ນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ມູນ XML ຈາກເນື້ອໃນ XML ທີ່ມີໂຄງສ້າງຕ່າງໆ ລົງໃນຫ້ອງຂອງເອກະສານສະເປຣດຊີດທີ່ມີຢູ່.</ahelp>"

#. QZ8zF
#: xml_source.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xml_source.xhp\n"
"par_id861521496523519\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The XML Source feature allows XML content to be imported either partially or in full, depending on the structure of the XML content and the map definitions that the user defines. The user can specify multiple non-overlapping sub-structures to be mapped to different cell positions within the same document. The user can import either element contents, attribute values or both."
msgstr "ຄຸນສົມບັດແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ XML ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ນຳເຂົ້າເນື້ອໃນ XML ໄດ້ທັງໝົດ ຫຼື ບາງສ່ວນ ໂດຍອີງຕາມໂຄງສ້າງ ແລະ ການກຳນົດຜັງທີ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຕັ້ງໄວ້. ຜູ້ໃຊ້ສາມາດກຳນົດໂຄງສ້າງຍ່ອຍຫຼາຍອັນເພື່ອເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບຕຳແໜ່ງຫ້ອງຕ່າງໆໃນເອກະສານດຽວກັນໄດ້."

#. m8sWR
#: xml_source.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xml_source.xhp\n"
"hd_id801521494731764\n"
"help.text"
msgid "XML Source Dialog"
msgstr "ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ XML"

#. MZB9H
#: xml_source.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xml_source.xhp\n"
"par_id291521494762812\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The dialog consists of four parts."
msgstr "ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບປະກອບມີສີ່ສ່ວນ."

#. w7NoA
#: xml_source.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xml_source.xhp\n"
"hd_id601521494755603\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Source file"
msgstr "ໄຟລ໌ຕົ້ນທາງ"

#. dSeBP
#: xml_source.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xml_source.xhp\n"
"par_id161521494769832\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This lets you specify the path to the XML file that you wish to import into your document."
msgstr "ສ່ວນນີ້ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານກຳນົດທີ່ຢູ່ຂອງໄຟລ໌ XML ທີ່ຕ້ອງການນຳເຂົ້າ."

#. hcfNL
#: xml_source.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xml_source.xhp\n"
"hd_id491521494788029\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Map to Document"
msgstr "ຜັງເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບເອກະສານ"

#. RpAuk
#: xml_source.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xml_source.xhp\n"
"par_id211521494776007\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This pane shows the structure of the source XML content as a tree. This is initially empty, and gets populated when you specify the source file."
msgstr "ຊ່ອງນີ້ສະແດງໂຄງສ້າງຂອງເນື້ອໃນ XML ຕົ້ນທາງໃນຮູບແບບຕົ້ນໄມ້. ມັນຈະວ່າງເປົ່າໃນຕອນທຳອິດ ແລະ ຈະສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນເມື່ອທ່ານເລືອກໄຟລ໌ຕົ້ນທາງ."

#. dBEwr
#: xml_source.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xml_source.xhp\n"
"par_id161521494796604\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Each element in the tree can be one of three types:"
msgstr "ແຕ່ລະອົງປະກອບໃນຕົ້ນໄມ້ສາມາດເປັນໜຶ່ງໃນສາມປະເພດນີ້:"

#. T65DV
#: xml_source.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xml_source.xhp\n"
"par_id931521494810426\n"
"help.text"
msgid "attribute, represented by the symbol <emph>@</emph>"
msgstr "ຄຸນລັກສະນະ (attribute), ແທນດ້ວຍສັນຍະລັກ <emph>@</emph>"

#. xkror
#: xml_source.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xml_source.xhp\n"
"par_id521521494825665\n"
"help.text"
msgid "single non-recurring element, represented by the symbol <emph></></emph>, and"
msgstr "ອົງປະກອບດ່ຽວທີ່ບໍ່ເກີດຊ້ຳ, ແທນດ້ວຍສັນຍະລັກ <emph></></emph>, ແລະ"

#. ReEmy
#: xml_source.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xml_source.xhp\n"
"par_id691521494844848\n"
"help.text"
msgid "recurring element, represented by the symbol <emph><//></emph>."
msgstr "ອົງປະກອບທີ່ເກີດຊ້ຳ, ແທນດ້ວຍສັນຍະລັກ <emph><//></emph>."

#. WcNfX
#: xml_source.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xml_source.xhp\n"
"par_id451521494864514\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A non-recurring element is an element that can only occur once under the same parent. It is mapped to a single cell in the document."
msgstr "ອົງປະກອບທີ່ບໍ່ເກີດຊ້ຳ ແມ່ນອົງປະກອບທີ່ປະກົດໄດ້ພຽງຄັ້ງດຽວພາຍໃຕ້ຕົວຫຼັກດຽວກັນ. ມັນຈະຖືກເຊື່ອມໂຍງເຂົ້າກັບຫ້ອງດຽວໃນເອກະສານ."

#. WVC7K
#: xml_source.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xml_source.xhp\n"
"par_id361521494872103\n"
"help.text"
msgid "A recurring element is an element that can appear multiple times under the same parent. It serves as an enclosing parent of a single record entry of multiple record entries. These entries are imported into a range those height equals the number of entries plus one additional header row."
msgstr "ອົງປະກອບທີ່ເກີດຊ້ຳ ແມ່ນອົງປະກອບທີ່ປະກົດໄດ້ຫຼາຍຄັ້ງ. ມັນຈະຖືກນຳເຂົ້າເປັນຊ່ວງຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ມີລວງສູງເທົ່າກັບຈຳນວນຂໍ້ມູນ ບວກກັບແຖວຫົວຂໍ້."

#. 3BFmD
#: xml_source.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xml_source.xhp\n"
"hd_id581521494885433\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Mapped cell"
msgstr "ຫ້ອງທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງ"

#. hPodi
#: xml_source.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xml_source.xhp\n"
"par_id661521494897796\n"
"help.text"
msgid "This field specifies the position of a cell in the document that an element or an attribute is linked to. If it is a non-recurring element or an attribute, it simply points to the cell where the value of the linked element/attribute will get imported. If it is a recurring element, it points to the top-left cell of the range where the whole record entries plus header will get imported."
msgstr "ຊ່ອງນີ້ກຳນົດຕຳແໜ່ງຂອງຫ້ອງໃນເອກະສານທີ່ຈະເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບອົງປະກອບ XML."

#. ipMuD
#: xml_source.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xml_source.xhp\n"
"hd_id151521553082338\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Import"
msgstr "ນຳເຂົ້າ"

#. LrH8y
#: xml_source.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xml_source.xhp\n"
"par_id131521553077261\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Pressing the Import button starts the import process based on the link definitions that the user has provided. Once the import finishes, the dialog will close."
msgstr "ການກົດປຸ່ມ 'ນຳເຂົ້າ' ຈະເລີ່ມຂະບວນການນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ມູນຕາມທີ່ໄດ້ກຳນົດໄວ້. ເມື່ອສຳເລັດແລ້ວ ກ່ອງໂຕ້ຕອບຈະປິດລົງ."

#. nfBjK
#: xml_source.xhp
msgctxt ""
"xml_source.xhp\n"
"par_id240920171007419799\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<link href=\"https://wiki.documentfoundation.org/Development/Calc/XMLSource\" target=\"_blank\">Wiki page on XML Source</link>"
msgstr "<link href=\"https://wiki.documentfoundation.org/Development/Calc/XMLSource\" target=\"_blank\">ໜ້າ Wiki ກ່ຽວກັບແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ XML</link>"

#. sYwVm
#: zoom.xhp
msgctxt ""
"zoom.xhp\n"
"tit\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Zoom"
msgstr "ຊູມ (ຍໍ້/ຂະຫຍາຍ)"

#. BFTKX
#: zoom.xhp
msgctxt ""
"zoom.xhp\n"
"bm_id61678279382558\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<bookmark_value>Zoom;spreadsheet</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>Zoom in;spreadsheet</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>Zoom out;spreadsheet</bookmark_value>"
msgstr "<bookmark_value>ຊູມ;ສະເປຣດຊີດ</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>ຂະຫຍາຍ;ສະເປຣດຊີດ</bookmark_value>    <bookmark_value>ຍໍ້;ສະເປຣດຊີດ</bookmark_value>"

#. FvoRD
#: zoom.xhp
msgctxt ""
"zoom.xhp\n"
"hd_id301674151617149\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<variable id=\"h1\"><link href=\"text/scalc/01/zoom.xhp\">Zooming In and Out in Calc</link></variable>"
msgstr "<variable id=\"h1\"><link href=\"text/scalc/01/zoom.xhp\">ການຍໍ້ ແລະ ຂະຫຍາຍໃນ Calc</link></variable>"

#. DYtFG
#: zoom.xhp
msgctxt ""
"zoom.xhp\n"
"par_id841674151617153\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Zoom allows users to magnify and reduce the screen display. Multiple methods of zooming in and out are available in Calc."
msgstr "ການຊູມຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້ສາມາດຂະຫຍາຍ ແລະ ຍໍ້ການສະແດງຜົນໜ້າຈໍໄດ້. ໃນ Calc ມີຫຼາຍວິທີໃນການຍໍ້ ແລະ ຂະຫຍາຍ."

#. eqb5j
#: zoom.xhp
msgctxt ""
"zoom.xhp\n"
"par_id91678230156720\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose menu <menuitem>View - Zoom</menuitem>, and select the magnification value in the submenu."
msgstr "ເລືອກເມນູ <menuitem>ມຸມມອງ - ຊູມ</menuitem>, ແລ້ວເລືອກຄ່າການຂະຫຍາຍໃນເມນູຍ່ອຍ."

#. M3VFu
#: zoom.xhp
msgctxt ""
"zoom.xhp\n"
"par_id421678230024566\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Click the plus (or minus) icon on the zoom slider in the status bar. The screen size increases (or decreases) by 10% with each click."
msgstr "ກົດໃສ່ໄອຄອນບວກ (ຫຼື ລົບ) ຢູ່ແຖບເລື່ອນຊູມໃນແຖບສະຖານະ. ຂະໜາດໜ້າຈໍຈະເພີ່ມຂຶ້ນ (ຫຼື ຫຼຸດລົງ) ເທື່ອລະ 10% ຕໍ່ການກົດໜຶ່ງຄັ້ງ."

#. ZLGvd
#: zoom.xhp
msgctxt ""
"zoom.xhp\n"
"par_id511678230735657\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Drag the Zoom slider handle to adjust the magnification factor with the mouse."
msgstr "ລາກປຸ່ມເລື່ອນຊູມເພື່ອປັບລະດັບການຂະຫຍາຍດ້ວຍເມົາສ໌."

#. GrFgu
#: zoom.xhp
msgctxt ""
"zoom.xhp\n"
"par_id461674152484428\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline> while rolling the mouse wheel."
msgstr "ກົດປຸ່ມ <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>Ctrl</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline> ຄ້າງໄວ້ໃນຂະນະທີ່ປິ່ນລໍ້ເມົາສ໌."

#. hnANA
#: zoom.xhp
msgctxt ""
"zoom.xhp\n"
"par_id71678262942683\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<image src=\"media/helpimg/scalc/calczoomslider.png\" id=\"img_id721678262942684\" width=\"282px\" height=\"40px\"><alt id=\"alt_id461678262942685\">Calc Zoom Slider</alt></image>"
msgstr "<image src=\"media/helpimg/scalc/calczoomslider.png\" id=\"img_id721678262942684\" width=\"282px\" height=\"40px\"><alt id=\"alt_id461678262942685\">ແຖບເລື່ອນການຊູມຂອງ Calc</alt></image>"

#. 3svKV
#: zoom.xhp
msgctxt ""
"zoom.xhp\n"
"par_id41678230455376\n"
"help.text"
msgid "20% is the minimum zoom factor. 400% is the maximum."
msgstr "20% ແມ່ນລະດັບການຊູມຕໍ່າສຸດ. 400% ແມ່ນລະດັບສູງສຸດ."

#. DpeBz
#: zoom.xhp
msgctxt ""
"zoom.xhp\n"
"hd_id101678230496709\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Zooming with the Zoom slider"
msgstr "ການຊູມດ້ວຍແຖບເລື່ອນຊູມ"

#. DzEnz
#: zoom.xhp
msgctxt ""
"zoom.xhp\n"
"par_id361678230881080\n"
"help.text"
msgid "In addition to the slider plus and minus icons, you can drag the slider handle to manually adjust the zoom factor."
msgstr "ນອກຈາກໄອຄອນບວກ ແລະ ລົບແລ້ວ, ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດລາກປຸ່ມເລື່ອນເພື່ອປັບລະດັບການຊູມດ້ວຍຕົນເອງໄດ້."

#. CabnS
#: zoom.xhp
msgctxt ""
"zoom.xhp\n"
"par_id531678230887813\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Also, click anywhere on the slider to adjust the zoom factor."
msgstr "ນອກນັ້ນ, ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດກົດໃສ່ບ່ອນໃດກໍໄດ້ໃນແຖບເລື່ອນເພື່ອປັບລະດັບການຊູມ."

#. dWykD
#: zoom.xhp
msgctxt ""
"zoom.xhp\n"
"par_id841678230875046\n"
"help.text"
msgid "The center line on the zoom slider represents 100% zoom factor."
msgstr "ເສັ້ນຢູ່ເຄິ່ງກາງຂອງແຖບເລື່ອນຊູມໝາຍເຖິງລະດັບການຊູມ 100%."

#. GrGzC
#: zoom.xhp
msgctxt ""
"zoom.xhp\n"
"hd_id631678233685940\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Access Zoom via the menu"
msgstr "ການເຂົ້າເຖິງການຊູມຜ່ານເມນູ"

#. MS7p5
#: zoom.xhp
msgctxt ""
"zoom.xhp\n"
"par_id501678233750773\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose menu <menuitem>View – Zoom</menuitem>. The predefined options are:"
msgstr "ເລືອກເມນູ <menuitem>ມຸມມອງ – ຊູມ</menuitem>. ຕົວເລືອກທີ່ມີໃຫ້ແລ້ວມີດັ່ງນີ້:"

#. xCqjf
#: zoom.xhp
msgctxt ""
"zoom.xhp\n"
"par_id391678233854552\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<menuitem>Entire Page</menuitem>: resizes the display to fit the width and height of the page."
msgstr "<menuitem>ທັງໜ້າ</menuitem>: ປັບຂະໜາດການສະແດງຜົນໃຫ້ພໍດີກັບຄວາມກວ້າງ ແລະ ຄວາມສູງຂອງໜ້າ."

#. k8CEL
#: zoom.xhp
msgctxt ""
"zoom.xhp\n"
"par_id31678233860361\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<menuitem>Page Width</menuitem>: resizes the display to fit the width of the page, limited to the minimum and maximum zoom factor. The top and bottom edges of the selection may not be visible."
msgstr "<menuitem>ຄວາມກວ້າງໜ້າ</menuitem>: ປັບຂະໜາດການສະແດງຜົນໃຫ້ພໍດີກັບຄວາມກວ້າງຂອງໜ້າ."

#. dG4GA
#: zoom.xhp
msgctxt ""
"zoom.xhp\n"
"par_id681678233866236\n"
"help.text"
msgid "<menuitem>Optimal View</menuitem>: resizes the display to fit the width and height of the selected cells. The enlargement or reduction are limited to the minimum and maximum zoom factors. If only one cell is selected then it will zoom to 100%."
msgstr "<menuitem>ມຸມມອງທີ່ເໝາະສົມ</menuitem>: ປັບຂະໜາດການສະແດງຜົນໃຫ້ພໍດີກັບຄວາມກວ້າງ ແລະ ຄວາມສູງຂອງຫ້ອງທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້."

